%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Hard%20work%20will%20never%20go%20unrewarded%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%20Mission%3A%3Cbr%3E%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3Vikram%20soft-landed%20on%20%F0%9F%8C%96%2C%20again!%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EVikram%20Lander%20exceeded%20its%20mission%20objectives.%20It%20successfully%20underwent%20a%20hop%20experiment.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOn%20command%2C%20it%20fired%20the%20engines%2C%20elevated%20itself%20by%20about%2040%20cm%20as%20expected%20and%20landed%20safely%20at%20a%20distance%20of%2030%20%E2%80%93%2040%20cm%20away.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FT63t3MVUvI%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FT63t3MVUvI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1698570774385205621%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%204%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EVeeramuthuvel%E2%80%99s%20career%20began%20at%20Lakshmi%20Machine%20Works%20in%20Coimbatore%2C%20where%20he%20developed%20a%20deep%20interest%20in%20aerospace%20engineering.%20Subsequently%2C%20he%20worked%20in%20the%20research%20and%20development%20division%20of%20the%20helicopter%20division%20of%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Limited%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331067%2Framji-swaminathan-craftizan-miniature-models-of-isro-rockets-satellites-chandrayaan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesign%20engineer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20dreamt%20of%20working%20in%20ISRO%20since%20his%20college%20days%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20ISRO%20Satellite%20Centre%20as%20a%20project%20engineer%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20he%20worked%20on%20multiple%20remote%20sensing%20and%20scientific%20satellites%2C%20and%20with%20the%20Mars%20Orbiter%20Mission%20in%202013.%20He%20also%20enrolled%20in%20a%20PhD%20at%20IIT%20Madras%20to%20fuel%20his%20love%20for%20research%20after%20joining%20ISRO.%20His%20doctorate%20is%20on%20the%20topic%20%E2%80%98Vibration%20Suppression%20of%20Electronic%20Package%20in%20Satellites%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVeeramuthuvel%20led%20ISRO%E2%80%99s%20inaugural%20nanosatellite%20team%2C%20successfully%20launching%20three%20of%20them.%20With%20a%20team%20of%20young%20scientists%2C%20all%20under%20the%20age%20of%2040%2C%20they%20achieved%20this%20feat%20in%20just%20nine%20months%2C%20propelling%20Veeramuthuvel%20to%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%2015%20to%2020%20%5Bscientists%5D%20and%20they%20came%20up%20with%20a%20bus%20configuration%20for%20the%20project%2C%20which%20was%20launched%20around%202017.%20This%20was%20the%20time%20we%20saw%20his%20leadership%20qualities%20and%20that%20helped%20him%20emerge%20as%20the%20project%20director%20after%20the%20failure%20of%20Chandrayaan-2%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20former%20ISRO%20scientist%20and%20satellite%20centre%20director%20M%20Annadurai%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20that%2C%20Veeramuthuvel%20was%20appointed%20as%20an%20associate%20project%20director%20for%20the%20Chandrayaan-2%20mission%20and%20later%20promoted%20to%20the%20role%20of%20project%20director%20for%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20where%20he%20led%20a%20substantial%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324699%2Fawais-ahmed-founded-space-startup-pixxel-hyperspectral-satellite-launch-hyperloop-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20humble%20scientist%20%3C%2Fa%3Esays%20that%20one%20must%20make%20use%20of%20their%20opportunities%20well%20to%20reach%20the%20top.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20simple%20person.%20If%20I%20am%20able%20to%20achieve%20these%20things%20and%20reach%20this%20level%2C%20everyone%20else%20can%20do%20it%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E