20to%20stop%20the%20crimes%20of%20the%20Zionist%20regime%20against%20the%20oppressed%20Palestinian%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20Iranian%20President%20Ebrahim%20Raisi%20told%20his%20Syrian%20counterpart%2C%20Bashar%20al-Assad%2C%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20Nournews%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20presidents%20stressed%20their%20support%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20the%20Syrian%20state%20news%20agency%20SANA%20reported.%20Assad%20urged%20swift%20action%20on%20the%20Arab%20and%20Islamic%20levels%20to%20protect%20the%20Palestinian%20population%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Treat%20Hamas%20like%20ISIS%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20told%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20that%20Hamas%20will%20be%20%E2%80%9Ccrushed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20as%20ISIS%20was%20crushed%2C%20so%20too%20will%20Hamas%20be%20crushed.%20And%20Hamas%20should%20be%20treated%20exactly%20the%20way%20ISIS%20was%20treated%2C%E2%80%9D%20Netanyahu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBlinken%20told%20reporters%20there%20should%20be%20no%20ambiguity%20in%20condemning%20terror%20attacks%20against%20Israel%20and%20the%20Hamas%20%E2%80%9Creign%20of%20terror.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%2C%20Blinken%20added%2C%20does%20not%20represent%20Palestinians%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%9Clegitimate%20aspirations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20promise%20Israel%20the%20unequivocal%20support%20of%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20may%20be%20strong%20enough%20on%20your%20own%20to%20defend%20yourself.%20But%20as%20long%20as%20America%20exists%2C%20you%20will%20never%2C%20ever%20have%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20Blinken%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20always%20be%20there%20by%20your%20side.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEgypt%20says%20it%20%E2%80%98never%20closed%E2%80%99%20crossing%20to%20Gaza%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEgypt%20has%20called%20on%20those%20willing%20to%20send%20aid%20to%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20to%20deliver%20their%20assistance%20to%20the%20Arish%20International%20Airport%20in%20the%20Sinai%20Peninsula%2C%20denying%20its%20closure%20of%20the%20border%20crossing%20to%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Egyptian%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20Thursday%20statement%20that%20the%20airport%20will%20be%20receiving%20any%20international%20humanitarian%20aid%2C%20calling%20for%20%E2%80%9Caid%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20who%20face%20huge%20risks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECairo%20also%20denied%20earlier%20reports%20that%20it%20shuttered%20its%20Rafah%20border%20crossing%20with%20Gaza%2C%20saying%20the%20reports%20are%20%E2%80%9Cinaccurate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Rafah%20border%20crossing%20between%20Egypt%20and%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20is%20open%20for%20operation%20and%20has%20not%20been%20closed%20at%20any%20stage%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20crisis%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ministry%20said.%20It%20added%20that%20the%20Palestinian%20side%20of%20the%20crossing%20was%20destroyed%20due%20to%20repeated%20Israeli%20strikes%2C%20which%20disrupted%20its%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEgypt%20called%20on%20Israel%20to%20refrain%20from%20targeting%20the%20Palestinian%20side%20of%20the%20crossing%20to%20allow%20for%20the%20efforts%20to%20repair%20it%20and%20allow%20it%20to%20operate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20toll%20from%20the%20Hamas%20deadly%20weekend%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20and%20the%20subsequent%20Israeli%20bombardment%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20have%20continued%20to%20rise%2C%20with%20over%202%2C500%20killed%20since%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20public%20broadcaster%20Kan%20said%20at%20least%201%2C300%20were%20killed%20since%20the%20attack%2C%20with%203%2C300%20more%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20Health%20Ministry%20in%20Gaza%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20said%201%2C203%20were%20killed%2C%20with%205%2C763%20more%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUN%20experts%20condemn%20%E2%80%98horrific%E2%80%99%20Hamas%20attack%2C%20Israeli%20%E2%80%98collective%20punishment%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20United%20Nations%20independent%C2%A0experts%20have%20condemned%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20deadly%20weekend%20terror%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20as%20%E2%80%9Chorrific%E2%80%9D%20and%20decried%20%E2%80%9Cindiscriminate%20military%20attacks%E2%80%9D%20by%20Israel%20hitting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgaza%2Ft-19074241%5C%22%3Ethe%20Gaza%20Strip%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20%5BPalestinians%20in%20Gaza%5D%20have%20lived%20under%20unlawful%20blockade%20for%2016%20years%2C%20and%20already%20gone%20through%20five%20major%20brutal%20wars%2C%20which%20remain%20unaccounted%20for%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20group%2C%20which%20includes%20several%20UN%C2%A0special%20rapporteurs%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20independent%20experts%2C%20who%20are%20mandated%20by%20the%20UN%20but%20do%20not%20speak%20on%20its%20behalf%2C%20described%20the%20attacks%20on%20Gaza%20as%20%E2%80%9Ccollective%20punishment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20justification%20for%20violence%20that%20indiscriminately%20targets%20innocent%20civilians%2C%20whether%20by%20Hamas%20or%20Israeli%20forces.%20This%20is%20absolutely%20prohibited%20under%20international%20law%20and%20amounts%20to%20a%20war%20crime%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20military%20spokesman%20Richard%20Hecht%20denied%20Israeli%20forces%20were%20%E2%80%9Ccarpet%20bombing%E2%80%9D%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20which%20is%20ruled%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhamas%2Ft-19034915%5C%22%3EHamas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20on%20the%20besieged%20Palestinian%20strip%20were%20%E2%80%9Cbigger%E2%80%9D%20than%20ever%20before.%20Hecht%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20the%20targeting%20of%20struck%20sites%20is%20based%20on%20intelligence%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20was%20receiving%20specific%20information%20in%20each%20case%20about%20where%20Palestinian%20militants%20were%20heading%2C%20Hecht%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20attacks%20were%20focused%20on%20destroying%20the%20infrastructure%20of%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20announced%20it%20will%20not%20allow%20humanitarian%20aid%20or%20basic%20resources%2C%20including%20water%2C%20electricity%20and%20fuel%2C%20to%20the%20besieged%20Gaza%20Strip%20until%20its%20Hamas%20rulers%20release%20hostages%20abducted%20during%20their%C2%A0deadly%20weekend%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHumanitarian%20aid%20to%20Gaza%3F%20No%20electric%20switch%20will%20be%20turned%20on%2C%20no%20water%20tap%20will%20be%20opened%20and%20no%20fuel%20truck%20will%20enter%20until%20the%20Israeli%20abductees%20are%20returned%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20Israeli%20Energy%20Minister%20Israel%20Katz%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flogs1279.xiti.com%2Fhit.xiti%3Fs%3D531599%26s2%3D2%26p%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%3A%3Athewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26di%3D%26an%3D%26ac%3D%26x1%3D1%26x2%3D2%26x5%3Dthewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26x6%3D1%26x8%3Den-VAS-Volltexte-JavaScript-thewire.in-dwde%26x10%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697118050000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12190520%2FScreenshot-2023-10-12-at-7.04.38%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22http