20market%20demands%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20EV5%20comes%20with%20two%2012.3-inch%20(31-centimeter)%20screens%20for%20instrument%20displays%20and%20infotainment%2C%20and%20a%205-inch%20climate%20control%20display.%20The%20Chinese%20version%20will%20have%20a%20front%20bench%20seat%2C%20while%20the%20rear%20seat%20can%20be%20folded%20flat%20to%20transform%20into%20a%20bed.%20There%20is%20also%20a%204-liter%20(1.1%20gallon)%20refrigerator%20and%20warming%20unit%20for%20storing%20food%20and%20drinks.%20The%20cars%20will%20be%20made%20at%20factories%20in%20China%20and%20Korea%2C%20with%20production%20starting%20around%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKia%20also%20displayed%20two%20concept%20cars%20-%20the%20EV3%2C%20a%20compact%20version%20of%20its%20flagship%20EV9%3B%20and%20the%20EV4%2C%20a%20four-door%20sedan%20that%20looks%20more%20like%20a%20sports%20car.%20The%20three%20models%20are%20part%20of%20Kia's%20plan%20to%20introduce%20smaller%20EVs%20ranging%20in%20price%20from%20%2435%2C000%20to%20%2450%2C000%20to%20accelerate%20the%20widespread%20adoption%20of%20battery-powered%20cars%2C%20the%20company%20said.%20Top-end%20models%20will%20go%20for%20up%20to%20%2480%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKia%20last%20month%20introduced%20its%20cheapest%20EV%20-%20the%20single-seat%20Ray%2C%20which%20starts%20at%20%2420%2C000%20and%20is%20only%20available%20in%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETesla%20Inc.%20started%20selling%20its%20Chinese-made%20Model%20Y%20SUV%20in%20Korea%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20priced%20from%20about%2057%20million%20won%20(%2442%2C550).%20With%20government%20subsidies%2C%20the%20price%20drops%20to%20about%20%2437%2C000%20in%20Seoul%20and%20as%20low%20as%20%2430%2C000%20in%20some%20cities%20that%20offer%20extra%20incentives%20for%20EVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESmaller%20EVs%20are%20Kia's%20%26quot%3Bentry%20to%20the%20segment%20of%20customers%26quot%3B%20who%20look%20for%20affordable%20electric%20cars%20with%20lower%20prices%20and%20charging%20convenience%2C%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Ho%20Sung%20Song%20told%20reporters%20at%20the%20EV%20Day%2C%20held%20in%20Yeoju%20city%2C%20southeast%20of%20Seoul.%20The%20automaker%20aims%20to%20sell%201.6%20million%20EVs%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20meet%20that%20target%2C%20Kia%20plans%20to%20have%20eight%20production%20facilities%20by%202025.%20In%20Europe%2C%20the%20company%20will%20focus%20on%20making%20small-%20and%20medium-size%20EVs%2C%20while%20it%20will%20produce%20mid-%20and%20large-sized%20vehicles%20in%20China.%20In%20India%2C%20it%20will%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Bstrategically%20designed%20EV%20models%20tailored%20for%20emerging%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Ho%20Sung%20Song%20said%2C%20without%20elaborating.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKia%20has%20to%20study%20%26quot%3Bvery%20deeply%26quot%3B%20how%20to%20cut%20EV%20prices%20further%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20very%20important%20for%20us%3B%20how%20we%20can%20make%20the%20vehicles%20below%20around%20%2425%2C000%20in%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20in%20the%20future%2C%20we%20need%20some%20different%20sales%20strategies%2C%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20selling%20vehicles%20without%20a%20battery%2C%20which%20buyers%20can%20then%20rent%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrices%20of%20batteries%2C%20the%20most%20expensive%20part%20of%20an%20EV%2C%20are%20expected%20to%20fall%20to%20%2499%20per%20kWh%20by%202025%20as%20technology%20improves%20and%20new%20lithium%20reserves%20are%20developed%2C%20according%20to%20an%20Oct.%204%20report%20by%20Goldman%20Sachs%20Group%20Inc.%20analysts%20led%20by%20Kota%20Yuzawa.%20He%20upgraded%20Kia's%20stock%20to%20a%20buy%20on%20improving%20margins%20as%20battery%20costs%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKia%20and%20affiliate%20Hyundai%20Motor%20Co.%20sold%20around%20374%2C000%20EVs%20in%20the%20first%20eight%20months%20of%202023%2C%20ranking%20seventh%20globally%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20from%20SNE%20Research.%20Their%20combined%20market%20share%20of%20the%20global%20EV%20market%2C%20including%20electric%20and%20plug-in%20hybrid%20vehicles%2C%20has%20fallen%20to%204.3%25%20this%20year%20from%205.4%25%20in%202022%2C%20due%20to%20the%20strong%20growth%20of%20China's%20BYD%20Co.%2C%20the%20research%20group%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHo%20Sung%20Song%20said%20Kia%20may%20introduce%20a%20compact%20model%20EV2%20in%20Europe.%20The%20European%20Union%20has%20started%20a%20probe%20into%20China's%20EV%20subsidies%2C%20which%20could%20result%20on%20tariffs%20being%20imposed%20on%20made-in-China%20cars%20and%20potentially%20benefit%20the%20Korean%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEV2%20is%20very%20unique%2C%20very%20important%20model%20for%20European%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BEV2%20is%20very%20European%20style%20and%20it%20will%20be%20produced%20in%20Europe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697115300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fg1jas7mo_kia-bed-ev-bloomberg_625x300_12_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcar-or-bedroom-with-a-fridge-see-kias-newest-ev-4475240%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kia%20Corp.%20unveiled%20a%20compact%20electric%20sport-utility%20vehicle%20and%20two%20concept%20EVs%20as%20it%20builds%20out%20a%20range%20of%20cheaper%20models%20to%20appeal%20to%20budget-conscious%20drivers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcar-or-bedroom-with-a-fridge-see-kias-newest-ev-4475240%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcar-or-bedroom-with-a-fridge-see-kias-newest-ev-4475240%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcar-or-bedroom-wit