%2C200%20Israelis%20died%20in%20the%20terror%20attack%20and%201%2C500%20Hamas%20fighters%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20Israeli%20counterattack.%20At%20least%201%2C300%20residents%20of%20Gaza%20Strip%20have%20died%20in%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20that%20flattened%20several%20large%20building%20into%20heaps%20of%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20today%20said%20it%20is%20ready%20for%20the%20ground%20assault%20on%20Hamas%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20but%20the%20country's%20political%20leaders%20had%20not%20yet%20taken%20a%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20waiting%20to%20see%20what%20our%20political%20leadership%20decides%20about%20a%20potential%20ground%20incursion%2C%26quot%3B%20army%20spokesman%20Richard%20Hecht%20told%20journalists%2C%20news%20agency%20AFP%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Israelis%20roll%20into%20Gaza%20Strip%20with%20a%20mechanised%20infantry%20force%20along%20with%20air%20support%20from%20attack%20helicopters%2C%20a%20fierce%20form%20of%20urban%20warfare%20will%20break%20out%20on%20the%20narrow%20streets%20and%20lanes%20of%20the%20seaside%20area%2C%20where%20the%20population%20is%20a%20huge%205%2C500%20people%20per%20square%20kilometre%20(sqkm)%20compared%20to%20Israel's%20400%20people%20per%20sqkm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETactical%20challenges%20for%20Israeli%20ground%20forces%20in%20Gaza%20Strip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EBuildings%20in%20Gaza%20Strip%20stand%20densely%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20space%20for%20such%20a%20huge%20population.%20The%20streets%20are%20narrow.%20It%20would%20be%20even%20more%20difficult%20for%20armoured%20personnel%20carriers%20(IFVs)%2C%20infantry%20fighting%20vehicles%20(IFVs)%20and%20tanks%20to%20navigate%20in%20Gaza%20Strip%20due%20to%20debris%20on%20the%20road%20from%20bombed%20out%20buildings.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EBooby%20traps%20in%20small%20spaces%20pose%20significant%20risks%20for%20Israeli%20troops%2C%20who%20will%20need%20to%20enter%2C%20verify%2C%20neutralise%20and%20clear%20buildings%20of%20Hamas%20group%20one%20at%20a%20time.%20Sniper%20attacks%20may%20come%20from%20any%20direction%20in%20Gaza%20Strip's%20maze%20of%20tall%20buildings%20that%20have%20small%2C%20dark%20windows.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20war%20in%20Syria%20and%20Ukraine%20have%20shown%20that%20a%20larger%20mechanised%20infantry%20force%20can%20be%20badly%20hurt%20by%20small%20teams%20using%20anti-tank%20guided%20missiles%20and%20rocket%20propelled%20grenades%20(RPGs)%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EInserting%20troops%20with%20helicopters%20will%20be%20risky%20as%20Hamas%20may%20have%20man-portable%20air%20defence%20system%20(MANPADS).%20Even%20unguided%20RPGs%20can%20be%20dangerous%20if%20the%20troop-transport%20helicopters%20fly%20too%20low.%20Two%20US%20helicopters%20were%20shot%20down%20in%20the%20Battle%20of%20Mogadishu%20in%201993%20while%20flying%20low%20and%20fast%20over%20the%20densely%20populated%20Somalian%20city%2C%20an%20incident%20that%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BBlack%20Hawk%20Down%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20media.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ELimiting%20collateral%20damage%20and%20civilian%20casualties%20will%20be%20a%20major%20challenge%20if%20Israeli%20troops%20enter%20Gaza%20Strip%20for%20an%20all-out%20assault.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cp%3EFears%20have%20grown%20for%20Gaza's%202.4%20million%20residents%20now%20enduring%20the%20fifth%20war%20in%2015%20years%20in%20the%20long-blockaded%20territory%2C%20which%20has%20also%20seen%20Israel%20cut%20off%20water%2C%20food%20and%20power%20supplies.%20Israeli%20Energy%20Minister%20Israel%20Katz%20vowed%20that%20the%20total%20siege%20of%20Gaza%20would%20continue%20until%20nearly%20150%20Israeli%20hostages%20are%20freed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHumanitarian%20aid%20to%20Gaza%3F%20No%20electric%20switch%20will%20be%20turned%20on%2C%20no%20water%20tap%20will%20be%20opened%20and%20no%20fuel%20truck%20will%20enter%20until%20the%20Israeli%20abductees%20are%20returned%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697114880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fanagqni_israel-army_625x300_12_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F5-tactical-challenges-for-israel-as-its-troops-prep-to-enter-gaza-strip-4474896%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israeli%20ground%20forces%20are%20ready%20to%20enter%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20densely%20populated%20places%20in%20the%20world%2C%20to%20fight%20the%20Hamas%20group%20that%20launched%20a%20massive%20terror%20attack%20on%20Saturday%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F5-tactical-challenges-for-israel-as-its-troops-prep-to-enter-gaza-strip-4474896%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F5-tactical-challenges-for-israel-as-its-troops-prep-to-enter-gaza-strip-4474896%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F5-tactical-challenges-for-israel-as-its-troops-prep-to-enter-gaza-strip-4474896%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22HCLTech%20Q2FY24%20result%3A%20Net%20profit%20up%209.9%25%20at%20Rs%203%2C883%20cr%3B%20attrition%20drops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697114628000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F12%2Ffull%2F1691816958-8493.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fhcltech-q2fy24-result-net-profit-up-9-9-at-rs-3-883-cr-attrition-drops-123101200969_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20consolidated%20revenue%20for%20the%20quarter%20grew%208.04%20per%20cent%20y-o-y%20at%20Rs%2026%2C672%20crore%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20Rs%2026%2C296%20crore%20in%20Q2FY23%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.co