22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESikkim%2C%20nestled%20within%20the%20Indian%20Himalayas%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20regions%20most%20vulnerable%20to%20global%20warming.%20Glaciers%20in%20the%20state%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarboncopy.info%2Fhow-climate-change-contributed-to-sikkim-floods%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eare%20melting%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20we%20had%20noted%20the%20accelerated%20rate%20at%20which%20Rathong%20Glacier%20was%20receding.%20Therefore%2C%20people%2C%20especially%20the%20scientific%20community%2C%20were%20up%20to%20speed%20with%20the%20issues%20of%20glacial%20lake%20outburst%20floods%20(GLOF)%20and%20the%20formation%20of%20many%20lakes%20on%20account%20of%20this%20phenomenon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20GLOF%20is%20a%20type%20of%20flood%20that%20occurs%20when%20a%20glacier-dammed%20lake%20breaches%20its%20natural%20barrier%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20sudden%20release%20of%20a%20large%20volume%20of%20water%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20early%20as%20September%202007%2C%20the%20then%20state%20government%20headed%20by%20Pawan%20Chamling%20had%20constituted%20a%20Glacier%20and%20Climate%20Change%20Commission%20(GCCC)%20to%20investigate%20this%20phenomenon.%20Noted%20glaciologist%20Dr%20S.%20Hasnain%20from%20The%20Energy%20and%20Resources%20Institute%20(TERI)%20led%20this%20programme%20formulated%20under%20the%20under%20the%20science%20and%20technology%20department%20of%20the%20Sikkim%20governmentThe%20Central%20Water%20Commission%2C%20a%20Government%20of%20India%20agency%2C%20has%20operated%20in%20Sikkim%20since%20the%20early%201970s.%20They%20had%20been%20commissioned%20by%20the%20then%20king%20of%20Sikkim%20to%20conduct%20a%20study%20on%20the%20river%20Teesta%20and%20its%20hydropower%20potential.%20They%20identified%20all%20the%20various%20stages%20of%20the%20Teesta.%20Teesta%20Stage%20III%20is%20the%20one%20that%20was%20affected%20by%20the%20GLOF%20in%20Chungthang.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20GLOF%20event%20is%20said%20to%20have%20started%20shortly%20before%20midnight%20on%20October%203%20in%20Lhonak%20Cho.%20This%20meant%20that%20the%20flood%20waters%20would%20have%20reached%20Chungthang%20in%20approximately%20one%20and%20a%20half%20hours.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20official%20confirmation%20about%20when%20the%20GLOF%20event%20started%20until%20satellite%20imagery%20reveals%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20flood%20was%20caused%20by%20a%20slide%20on%20one%20side%20of%20the%20lake%20pushing%20huge%20debris%20and%20ice%20into%20the%20water%20body%20which%20resulted%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98mini%20tsunami%E2%80%99.%20The%20Chungthang%20dam%20breached%20sometime%20after%20midnight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20now%20important%20is%20to%20find%20out%20why%20the%20manual%20alerting%20system%20failed%20in%20view%20of%20no%20early%20warning%20systems%20(EWS)%20in%20place.%20Indicator%20systems%20installed%20were%20nonfunctional.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChief%20minister%20P.S.%20Tamang%20has%20gone%20on%20record%20to%20state%20that%20he%20received%20the%20information%20at%2010%3A40%20pm%20on%20October%203.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20oncoming%20flood%20took%20people%2C%20homes%2C%20soldiers%2C%20ammunition%2C%20bridges%20and%20trucks%20besides%20all%20else%20in%20its%20wake.%20Even%20more%20terrifying%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20water%20descended%20from%20over%2017%2C000%20ft%20to%20about%206%2C000%20ft%20over%20a%2068%20km%20stretch.%20This%20steep%20descent%20ensures%20the%20kind%20of%20kinetic%20force%20which%20resulted%20in%20such%20a%20heavy%20toll%20on%20the%20way%20down%20to%20Chungthang%2C%20devastating%20it%2C%20and%20then%20on%20to%20the%20Teesta%20Stage%20III%20dam%20which%20was%2C%20according%20to%20sources%2C%20operating%20at%20120%25%20capacity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05140822%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-04-at-7.12.12-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05140822%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-04-at-7.12.12-PM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05140822%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-04-at-7.12.12-PM-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05140822%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-04-at-7.12.12-PM-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678417%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20flooded%20banks%20of%20the%20Teesta%20in%20North%20Sikkim.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20dam%20officials%20were%20alerted%20too%20late%20and%20the%20spillway%20gates%20could%20not%20be%20lifted%20on%20time.%20Some%20bravehearts%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20trying%20to%20save%20the%20dam%20and%20their%20colleagues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20has%20tried%20to%20shift%20the%20blame%20and%20focus%20on%20the%20dam%20itself.%20He%20said%20that%20it%20was%20not%20built%20to%20the%20right%20specifications%20and%20accused%20the%20previous%20government%20of%20corruption.%20How%20he%20came%20to%20this%20conclusion%20is%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20guess.%20But%20this%20lack%20of%20statesmanship%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20hide%20his%20own%20follies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20forgotten%20that%20till%202009%20he%20was%20very%20much%20part%20of%20the%20Sikkim%20Democratic%20Front%20(SDF).%20Now%2C%20to%20shift%20the%20blame%20is%20purely%20to%20shift%20the%20focus%20from%20the%20operations%2C%20maintenance%2C%20and%20improper%20monitoring%20of%20Lhonak%20Cho%20by%20his%20government.%20This%2C%20despite%20the%20repeated%20warnings%20from%20the%20scientists%20and%20other%20institutions%20that%20are%20now%20coming%20out%20in%20the%20public%20view%20and%20discourse.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENevertheless%2C%20SDF%20has%20demanded%20a%20full%20enquiry%20and%20a%20forensic%20investigation%20into%20all%20potential%20causes%20behind%20the%20GLOF%20event%20and%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20dam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20question%20that%20remains%20unanswered%20is%20why%20the%20dam%20was%20running%20beyond%20its%20capacity%2C%20as%20alluded%20to%20by%20the%20chairman%20of%20Teesta%20Urja%20Ltd%2C%20Sunil%20Sarogi.%20The%20investigation%20also%20needs%20to%20look%20at%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20manual%20alarm%20system.%20It%20took%20an%20Indo-Tibetan%20Border%20Police%20(ITBP)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejawan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20sound%20the%20alert%20ostensibly%20at%2010%3A40%20pm%20%E2%80%93%20exactly%20when%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20said%20to%20have%20received%20the%20information.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20most%20serious%20question%20is%20this%3A%20Did%20the%20chief%20minister%20fail%20to%20understand%20the%20enormity%20and%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation%20when%20he%20received%20the%20information%20and%20took%20it%20lightly%3F%20He%20continued%20with%20his%20meetings%20despite%20the%20warnings%20and%20left%20Mangan%20only%20at%2012%3A30%20am.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20point%20the%20public%20are%20making%20in%20affected%20areas%20is%20that%20even%20if%20the%20warnings%20had%20reached%20the%20major%20hotspots%20half%20an%20hour%20earlier%20then%20many%20lives%20could%20have%20been%20saved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithout%20understanding%20the%20fundamentals%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20has%20tried%20to%20change%20the%20narrative%20to%20score%20political%20points%20against%20the%20principal%20opposition%20%E2%80%93%20SDF%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20state%20is%20reeling%20from%20a%20massive%20disaster.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20purely%20in%20line%20with%20what%20he%20has%20been%20doing%20as%20a%20countermeasure%20during%20these%20four%20and%20half%20years%20of%20failed%20governance.%20The%20best%20way%20out%20is%20always%20to%20blame%20a%20government%20that%20was%20in%20the%20saddle%20for%2025%20years!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20learned%20that%20a%20multidisciplinary%20committee%20is%20being%20set%20up%20to%20investigate%20the%20dam%20breach.%20While%20this%20is%20a%20positive%20step%2C%20it%20all%20depends%20on%20the%20terms%20of%20reference%2C%20which%20must%20be%20comprehensive.%20This%20is%20a%20national%20disaster%2C%20and%20we%20must%20look%20at%20it%20from%20that%20lens.%20The%20findings%20will%20be%20of%20vital%20importance%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20entire%20Himalayan%20region%20where%20many%20GLOF-related%20dangers%20lurk.%20These%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20border%20security%20issues%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20it%20is%20a%20wake-up%20call%20for%20the%20whole%20country%2C%20Sikkim%20and%20its%20people%20have%20paid%20a%20heavy%20price.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20must%20show%20more%20empathy%20at%20this%20time%20of%20grieving%20and%20not%20indulge%20in%20petty%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EP.D.%20Rai%2C%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20SDF%20Party%20and%20a%20two%20term%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP.%20The%20views%20expressed%20are%20purely%20personal%20and%20do%20not%20necessarily%20reflect%20the%20views%20of%20the%20SDF%20Party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697113814000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12171224%2FF7kYy-sakAAkPZ8.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-sikkim-cm-cannot-evade-responsibility-on-the-teesta-dam-breach%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20it%20is%20a%20wake-up%20call%20for%20the%20whole%20country%2C%20Sikkim%20and%20its%20people%20have%20paid%20a%20heavy%20price.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-sikkim-cm-cannot-evade-responsibility-on-the-teesta-dam-breach%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Diwali%20outfit%20inspo%2C%20courtesy%20Kriti%20Sanon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697113800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104370037%2Cimgsize-99464.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fdiwali-outfit-inspiration-courtesy-kriti-sanon%2Fphotostory%2F104370037.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104370037.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EDiwali%20outfit%20inspiration%2C%20courtesy%20Kriti%20Sanon%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fdiwali-outfit-inspiration-courtesy-kriti-sanon%2Fphotostory%2F104370037.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20Friends%20Build%20Ecofriendly%20Row%20Houses%20in%20Bengaluru%20With%20Gorgeous%20Ethnic%20Architecture%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20first%20rays%20of%20dawn%20creep%20up%20on%20the%20city%20of%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20distant%20roar%20fills%20the%20muted%20air.%20It%20is%20soon%20accom