20needed%20to%20carefully%20carry%20coordinated%20attacks%20by%20land%2C%20air%20and%20sea%2C%20as%20to%20build%20or%20smuggle%20in%20rockets%20and%20drones%20would%20have%20required%20hundreds%20of%20people%20working%20over%20months.%20Israeli%20intelligence%20services%20%E2%80%93%20as%20well%20as%20those%20of%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20European%20allies%20%E2%80%93%20picked%20up%20nothing.%20Even%20more%20importantly%2C%20once%20something%20of%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20attack%20became%20clear%2C%20the%20military%20reacted%20in%20a%20haphazard%20and%20chaotic%20fashion%2C%20losing%20time%20to%20respond.%20Writing%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Atlantic%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Andrew%20Exum%2C%20a%20former%20US%20military%20officer%20who%20served%20as%20deputy%20assistant%20secretary%20of%20defense%20for%20Middle%20East%20policy%20in%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Finternational%2Farchive%2F2023%2F10%2Fisraeli-military-vulnerable-war-hamas%2F675591%2F%5C%22%3Ementions%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Israel%20Defence%20Force%E2%80%99s%20(IDF%E2%80%99s)%20complacency%20and%20lack%20of%20discipline%2C%20and%20how%20the%20Hezbollah%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20after%20the%202006%20conflict%20with%20Israel%20%E2%80%93%20holds%20the%20IDF%20%E2%80%9Cin%20contempt%E2%80%9D%20because%20of%20these%20qualities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20A%20long-term%20political%20disaster%20heaped%20onto%20the%20IDF%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20commentators%20in%20Israel%20and%20elsewhere%20immediately%20mentioned%20the%201973%20war%20and%20the%20way%20the%20then%20Israeli%20prime%20minister%20Golda%20Meir%20had%20rebuffed%20outreach%20by%20Egyptian%20president%20Anwar%20Sadat.%20This%20convinced%20Sadat%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20recover%20the%20Sinai%20territories%20lost%20by%20Egypt%20in%20the%201967%20war%20was%20to%20go%20to%20war%20again.%20In%20that%20sense%2C%20both%20the%201973%20war%20and%20the%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20seem%20not%20just%20to%20be%20an%20intelligence%20failure%20but%20also%20a%20failure%20of%20the%20intelligence%20of%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25125403%2FNetanyahu.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25125403%2FNetanyahu.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25125403%2FNetanyahu-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25125403%2FNetanyahu-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664935%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Av%20Jolanda%20Flubacher%2FWORLD%20ECONOMIC%20FORUM%2Fswiss-image.ch.%20CC%20BY-SA%202.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20Israeli%20leader%20has%20been%20as%20steadfast%20in%20sidelining%20the%20Palestinian%20issue%20as%20Netanyahu.%20Even%20Golda%20Meir%E2%80%99s%20execrable%20remark%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20was%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20Palestinians%E2%80%9D%20existed%20alongside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fjpost.com%2Fisrael-news%2Farticle-753212%5C%22%3Ea%20realisation%20that%20a%20Palestinian%20state%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20to%20come%20into%20existence.%20Netanyahu%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20never%20acknowledged%20the%20need%20for%20such%20a%20thing.%20He%20called%20Yitzhak%20Rabin%2C%20who%20signed%20the%20Oslo%20Accords%20with%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fmarking-25-years-since-rabin-killing-netanyahu-says-he-is-now-pm-under-threat%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CNazi%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ctraitor%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20attended%20a%20rally%20with%20a%20coffin%20and%20noose%20for%20Rabin.%20The%20assassination%20of%20Rabin%20by%20Yigal%20Amir%20began%20the%20retreat%20from%20the%20principles%20of%20%E2%80%9Cland%20for%20peace%E2%80%9D.%20Instead%2C%20every%20Israeli%20government%20since%20Rabin%E2%80%99s%20assassination%20%E2%80%93%20many%20of%20them%20led%20by%20Netanyahu%20%E2%80%93%20has%20expanded%20the%20stealing%20of%20Palestinian%20land%20through%20the%20establishment%20of%20illegal%20%E2%80%9Csettlements%E2%80%9D%20in%20occupied%20territory%2C%20and%20the%20pursuit%20of%20a%20policy%20that%20many%20international%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.btselem.org%2Ftopic%2Fapartheid%5C%22%3EIsraelis%3C%2Fa%3E%20regard%20as%20apartheid.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20has%20been%20done%20under%20the%20idea%20that%20an%20%E2%80%98invincible%E2%80%99%20IDF%2C%20and%20a%20superior%20intelligence%20agency%20like%20the%20Mossad%20and%20Shin%20Bet%2C%20could%20isolate%20and%20suppress%20the%20Palestinians.%20To%20be%20fair%2C%20numerous%20IDF%20personnel%20and%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thegatekeepersfilm.com%2F%5C%22%3EShin%20Bet%20chiefs%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20explicitly%20stated%20that%20this%20form%20of%20use%20of%20the%20military%20is%20destroying%20it%20from%20within%20and%20that%20a%20political%20resolution%20of%20the%20Israeli-Palestinian%20conflict%20is%20a%20necessity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20War%20crimes%20are%20war%20crimes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20murder%20and%20kidnap%20of%20civilians%20is%20never%20justified.%20Never.%20The%20murder%20of%20around%20200%20people%20attending%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Foct%2F09%2Fhow-the-hamas-attack-on-the-supernova-festival-in-israel-unfolded%5C%22%3Ea%20rave%20party%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20so%20morally%20reprehensible%20as%20to%20reduce%20the%20meaning%20of%20the%20word%20to%20nothingness.%20Hamas%2C%20and%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20like%20any%20other%20group%20living%20under%20military%20occupation%2C%20have%20a%20right%20to%20resist.%20Hamas%20even%20has%20the%20right%20to%20take%20prisoners%20of%20war%20%E2%80%93%20as%20long%20as%20they%20are%20military%20personnel%20and%20treated%20humanely.%20There%20is%20no%20right%2C%20ever%2C%20to%20commit%20war%20crimes.%20This%20applies%20to%20Israel%20as%20well%2C%20which%20routinely%20assaults%2C%20kidnaps%2C%20tortures%2C%20and%20murders%20Palestinian%20civilians.%20Every%20single%20Palestinian%20held%20in%20Israeli%20jails%2C%20whether%20charged%20by%20military%20courts%20or%20under%20%E2%80%9Cadministrative%20detention%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20illegally%20held.%20International%20law%20forbids%20the%20removal%20of%20people%20from%20an%20area%20under%20military%20occupation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fkidnapping-civilians-from-israel-hamas-war-crime%5C%22%3ELet%20Us%20Be%20Clear%2C%20the%20Kidnapping%20of%20Civilians%20from%20Israel%20By%20Hamas%20is%20a%20War%20Crime%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJew%2C%20Arab%2C%20Muslim%2C%20Christian%2C%20atheist%2C%20whatever%2C%20none%20of%20that%20matters.%20Human%20rights%20apply%20to%20all%20humans%20or%20they%20are%20worth%20nothing.%20It%20is%20both%20remarkable%20and%20deeply%20sad%20that%20courageous%20Israelis%20like%20Haggai%20Matar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fgaza-attack-context-israelis%2F%5C%22%3Ecling%20to%20these%20concepts%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20try%20to%20hide%20from%20rocket%20fire.%20And%20past%20comprehension%20that%20commentators%20in%20the%20US%20and%20parts%20of%20Europe%20would%20exclude%20the%20long%20history%20of%20war%20crimes%20by%20Israelis%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20as%20the%20Israeli%20leadership%20explicitly%20carries%20out%20further%20war%20crimes%20like%20depriving%20a%20largely%20civilian%20population%20of%20water%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Foct%2F10%2F830-dead-in-gaza-since-saturday-as-shelling-hits-school-hospitals-and-homes%5C%22%3Ebombing%20schools%20and%20hospitals%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20%E2%80%98Western%E2%80%99%20hypocrisy%20has%20few%20buyers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOutside%20of%20the%20US%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20countries%20largely%20governed%20by%20the%20descendants%20of%20European%20males%2C%20nobody%20%E2%80%93%20with%20the%20possible%20exception%20of%20the%20obsequious%20Narendra%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20is%20willing%20to%20buy%20the%20idea%20that%20Palestinians%20are%20exclusively%20to%20blame.%20Even%20a%20number%20of%20organisations%20and%20groups%20in%20Europe%2C%20the%20US%2C%20and%20its%20allies%20are%20dissenting.%20The%20clearest%20indicator%20of%20this%20was%20the%20EU%20announcing%20that%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Foct%2F10%2Feu-aid-to-palestinians-will-not-be-cancelled-as-decision-reversed%5C%22%3Enot%20stopping%20humanitarian%20aid%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20issue%20was%20started%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Foct%2F09%2Feu-freeze-of-palestinian-funds-sparks-diplomatic-row%5C%22%3EOliv%C3%A9r%20V%C3%A1rhelyi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20commissioner%20in%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20who%20tweeted%20that%20the%20EU%20would%20cut%20off%20all%20trade.%20V%C3%A1rhelyi%20is%20well%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98attack%20dog%E2%80%99%20of%20Viktor%20Orban%20%E2%80%93%20the%20anti-democratic%2C%20sexist%2C%20racist%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2Feurope%2F20220727-holocaust-survivors-condemn-race-remarks-by-hungary-s-orban%5C%22%3Eanti-semitic%3C%2Fa%3E%20prime%20minister%20of%20Hungary.%20Of%20course%2C%20Orban%20was%20elected%20using%20the%20services%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeednews.com%2Farticle%2Fhnsgrassegger%2Fgeorge-soros-conspiracy-finkelstein-birnbaum-orban-netanyahu%5C%22%3Etwo%20political%20strategists%20from%20the%20US%20Republican%20Party%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20had%20helped%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20prime%20ministerial%20campaign%20in%201995.%20Their%20trump%20card%3A%20a%20campaign%20against%20George%20Soros%20%E2%80%93%20who%20had%20no%20presence%20in%20Hungary%20%E2%80%93%20full%20of%20anti-Semitic%20tropes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20act%20of%20breathtaking%20hypocrisy%20was%20the%20president%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Ffull-text-ukraine-president-zelenskys-speech-to-israeli-lawmakers%2F%5C%22%3Ecomparing%20the%20attack%20by%20Hamas%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%20Throughout%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20the%20comparisons%20between%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20willingness%20to%20eliminate%20the%20Ukrainian%20state%20or%20leave%20it%20as%20a%20pawn%20in%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20hands%20and%20the%20comparison%20between%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20policy%20and%20Israeli%20policies%20towards%20the%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20stark.%20If%20Ukrainians%20have%20a%20right%20to%20a%20state%20and%20a%20life%20of%20dignity%20not%20ruled%20by%20a%20neighbouring%20state%2C%20then%20so%20do%20the%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20India%20under%20Modi%20is%20no%20%E2%80%98voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20of%20its%20posturing%20at%20the%20recently%20concluded%20G20%20summit%20that%20it%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9CVoice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%E2%80%9D%2C%20India%20is%20out%20of%20step%20with%20other%20post-colonial%20countries.%20India%2C%20or%20at%20least%20the%20tweet%20by%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20conveyed%20only%20concern%20for%20Israelis.%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20governing%20party%2C%20the%20African%20National%20Congress%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fisrael-hamas-and-the-weakness-of-the-west%2Fa-67051502%5C%22%3Ed