-benjamin-netanyahus-2023-un-general-assembly-speech%2F0000018a-bd3c-d490-adca-fdff21270000%5C%22%3Ecrude%20posturing%20at%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20September%2022%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Palestinians%E2%80%A6%20should%20not%20have%20a%20veto%20over%20the%20%5Bpeace%5D%20process%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20Arab%20states%2C%20but%20the%20Saudi-Israel%20normalisation%20has%20only%20become%20a%20possible%20reality%20over%20the%20last%20two%20months.%20The%20planning%20for%20the%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20would%20likely%20have%20taken%20much%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20the%20so-called%20peace%20process%20with%20Arab%20states%20is%20between%20the%20Israeli%20government%20and%20despotic%20leaders.%20Such%20deals%20remain%20deeply%20unpopular%2C%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F09%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fmideast-palestine-support-gaza.html%5C%22%3Emany%20street%20rallies%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20attack%20with%20Hamas%20demonstrated.%20The%20only%20reason%20that%20Arab%20despots%20are%20able%20to%20take%20them%20forward%20is%20because%20of%20the%20reputation%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98invincibility%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20the%20total%20impunity%20it%20enjoys%20because%20of%20nuclear%20weapons%20and%20the%20unrestricted%20backing%20of%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20by%20Hamas%2C%20as%20heinous%20as%20it%20is%2C%20has%20destroyed%20that%20reputation.%20It%20has%20also%20shown%20up%20countries%20like%20Egypt%2C%20Syria%2C%20Saudi%20and%20others%20that%20spend%20greatly%20on%20weapons%20but%20have%20allowed%20themselves%20to%20be%20bullied%20into%20submission.%20It%20will%20be%20very%20hard%20for%20Arab%20states%20to%20blithely%20continue%20this%20process%20of%20%E2%80%9Cnormalisation%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20the%20Arab%20leaders%20are%20not%20going%20to%20forgive%20the%20Palestinians%20for%20showing%20that%20they%20are%20willing%20to%20fight%20despite%20the%20lack%20of