20you%20need%20to%20go%20out%20there%20and%20win%20in%20bigger%20games%20like%20these.%20I%20am%20sure%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20do%20that%20in%20days%20to%20come.%20I%20hope%20you%20play%20big%20knocks%20in%20big%20games%2C%26quot%3B%20Shoaib%20Akhtar%20said%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAkhtar%20also%20backed%20the%20Pakistan%20bowlers%20who%20conceded%20344%20runs.%20%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20bowling%20is%20concerned%2C%20I%20will%20supports%20them.%20I%20really%20want%20Pakistan%20to%20go%20out%20there%20and%20do%20well.%20I%20won't%20criticise%20Pakistan's%20bowling%20as%20I%20had%20said%20that%20these%20are%20our%20kids%20and%20will%20back%20them.%20These%20are%20not%20ODI%20bowlers%20yet.%20Bowling%2010%20overs%20is%20a%20different%20thing.%20We%20played%20just%2012%20ODIs%20last%20year.%20This%20same%20bowling%20unit%20will%20start%20to%20perform%20in%20the%20upcoming%20two%20or%20three%20matches.%20I%20can%20understand%20the%20disappointment%2C%20but%20don't%20give%20up%20on%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Akhtar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMohammad%20Rizwan%20and%20Abdullah%20Shafique%20clubbed%20centuries%20as%20Pakistan%20chased%20down%20the%20highest%20target%20in%20World%20Cup%20history%20to%20beat%20Sri%20Lanka%20by%20six%20wickets%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20diminutive%20Rizwan%20overcame%20leg%20cramps%20to%20score%20a%20121-ball%20131%20not%20out%20while%20Shafique%20hit%20a%20103-ball%20113%20as%20Pakistan%20overhauled%20their%20345-run%20target%20in%2048.2%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20victory%20gives%20Pakistan%20two%20wins%20in%20as%20many%20games%20and%20a%20huge%20boost%20in%20confidence%20ahead%20of%20their%20high-profile%20clash%20against%20India%20in%20Ahmedabad%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlways%20proud%20when%20you%20perform%20like%20that.%20It%20was%20difficult%20and%20when%20you%20chase%20like%20that%2C%20it's%20special%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rizwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20player%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%20had%20the%20belief%20we%20can%20chase%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20cramping%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BSometimes%20cramps%2C%20sometimes%20acting!%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESri%20Lanka's%20imposing%20total%20of%20344-9%20was%20built%20around%20brilliant%20hundreds%20from%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kusal%20Mendis%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64307-kusal-mendis-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKusal%20Mendis%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Sadeera%20Samarawickrama.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20with%20the%20way%20the%20wicket%20behaved%2C%20we%20were%2020-25%20runs%20short%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sri%20Lanka%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Dasun%20Shanaka%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59545-madagamagamage-dasun-shanaka-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDasun%20Shanaka%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERizwan%20cracked%20eight%20boundaries%20and%20three%20sixes%20while%20Shafique's%20knock%20had%20ten%20boundaries%20and%20three%20sixes%20as%20Pakistan%20improved%20on%20the%20previous%20highest%20World%20Cup%20chase%20of%20328%20by%20Ireland%20against%20England%20in%20Bangalore%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERizwan%20added%20a%20match-turning%20176%20run%20stand%20for%20the%20third%20wicket%20with%20Shafique%20and%20another%2095%20for%20the%20fourth%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Saud%20Shakeel%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F117166-saud-shakeel-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESaud%20Shakeel%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20made%20a%2030-ball%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERizwan%20and%20Shafique%20lifted%20Pakistan%20from%20a%20disastrous%20start%20in%20which%20they%20lost%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Imam-ul-Haq%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63529-imam-ul-haq-playerprofile%5C%22%3EImam-ul-Haq%3C%2Fa%3E%20(12)%20and%20skipper%20Babar%20Azam%20(ten)%20to%20pacer%20%3Ca%2