0Muslim%20men%20who%20brought%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20court.%20The%20next%20hearing%20in%20the%20case%20will%20be%20on%20October%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%203%2C%202022%2C%20in%20the%20Undhela%20village%20in%20Kheda%20district%2C%20a%20dispute%20broke%20out%20between%20the%20members%20of%20the%20local%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20communities%20as%20the%20latter%20objected%20to%20a%20garba%20event%20being%20held%20near%20a%20mosque.%20The%20argument%20led%20to%20a%20violent%20clash%20and%20seven%20people%20were%20reportedly%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20of%20the%20case%20alleged%20that%20%E2%80%9Caround%20150%20people%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Muslim%20group%20attacked%20the%20planned%20garba%20venue%20late%20at%20night%20by%20allegedly%20pelting%20stones%2C%20injuring%20some%20policemen.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20police%20arrested%2013%20men%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20day%20videos%20began%20making%20the%20rounds%20on%20social%20media%20showing%20police%20officers%2C%20later%20identified%20as%20being%20from%20the%20crime%20branch%2C%20tying%20the%20alleged%20attackers%20in%20the%20October%203%20violence%20to%20a%20poll%20and%20beating%20them%20with%20sticks%2C%20in%20full%20public%20view%20and%20amid%20cheers%20from%20the%20onlooking%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20videos%20on%20social%20media%20sparking%20massive%20outrage%2C%20senior%20police%20officials%20ordered%20an%20inquiry%20into%20the%20incident%20and%20against%20the%20policemen%20involved.%20Inspector%20A.V.%20Parmar%20and%20sub-inspector%20D.B.%20Kumavat%20were%20identified%20from%20the%20clip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVictims%20Jahirmiya%20Malek%20(62)%2C%20Maksudabanu%20Malek%20(45)%2C%20Sahadmiya%20Malek%20(23)%2C%20Sakilmiya%20Malek%20(24)%20and%20Shahidraja%20Malek%20(25)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fkheda-flogging-police-notice%5C%22%3Emoved%20a%20petition%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20the%20Gujarat%20high%2