22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnclat-chairman-calls-for-developing-mechanism-to-regulate-digital-markets-123101200329_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Let%20Us%20Be%20Clear%2C%20the%20Kidnapping%20of%20Civilians%20from%20Israel%20By%20Hamas%20is%20a%20War%20Crime%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12135727%2FParade_of_Palestinian_Mujahideen_12.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20together%20with%20many%20of%20our%20friends%20in%20Israel%2C%20we%20have%20repeatedly%20condemned%20the%20crimes%20that%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20has%20committed%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20population%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20the%20West%20Bank.%20We%20have%20worked%20to%20protect%20Palestinians%E2%80%99%20rights.%20We%20have%20called%20for%20the%20imposition%20of%20sanctions%20on%20Israel%2C%20and%20also%20for%20international%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBut%20it%20was%20not%20only%20the%20support%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20that%20created%20the%20connection%20between%20the%20two%20of%20us.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20we%20have%20worked%20together%20to%20try%20to%20reveal%20all%20the%20documents%20in%20Israel%20from%20its%20security%20and%20diplomatic%20relationship%20with%20the%20Pinochet%20regime%20in%20Chile%2C%20including%20any%20information%20that%20exists%20in%20Israel%20regarding%20Daniel%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20David%20Silberman%2C%20who%20was%20kidnapped%20and%20disappeared%20by%20the%20Pinochet%20regime%E2%80%99s%20intelligence%20agency%20(DINA)%2C%20which%20at%20the%20time%20was%20in%20good%20relationship%20with%20its%20Israeli%20counterpart%20(the%20Mossad).%20After%2049%20years%2C%20the%20fate%20of%20David%20is%20still%20unknown.%20The%20legal%20proceedings%20in%20Israel%20that%20were%20conducted%20together%20with%20another%20family%20of%20a%20disappeared%20Chilean%2C%20were%20all%20rejected%20in%20the%20Israeli%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ELast%20weekend%2C%20the%20citizens%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20were%20under%20a%20murderous%20and%20barbaric%20attack%2C%20with%20Hamas%20using%20the%20same%20tactics%20as%20ISIS.%20Hamas%20fighters%20raided%20an%20outdoor%20party%20attended%20by%20crowds%20of%20young%20Jews%2C%20took%20control%20of%20Jewish%20kibbutzim%20and%20towns%20and%20then%20went%20from%20house%20to%20house%20and%20slaughtered%20entire%20families%20at%20gunpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDuring%20the%20Hamas%20attack%2C%20it%20kidnapped%20an%20unknown%20number%20of%20elderly%20people%2C%20men%2C%20women%2C%20children%20and%20infants.%20Among%20the%20abductees%20there%20are%20Jews%20as%20well%20as%20non-Jews%2C%20some%20with%20non-Israeli%20citizenship.%20The%20photos%20and%20videos%20that%20have%20already%20been%20published%20on%20social%20media%20and%20in%20international%20media%20of%20kidnapped%20mothers%20with%20children%2C%20elderly%20women%2C%20and%20the%20body%20of%20a%20naked%20woman%20are%20shocking%20and%20devastating.%20As%20with%20ISIS%2C%20Hamas%20fighters%20displayed%20the%20kidnapped%20women%20and%20drove%20around%20with%20them%20in%20the%20cities%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHamas%20is%20hiding%20the%20identity%20of%20most%20of%20the%20abductees%2C%20their%20location%2C%20their%20medical%20condition%20and%20their%20fate.%20The%20abductees%20are%20defined%20according%20to%20international%20law%20as%20victims%20of%20enforced%20disappearance.%20That%20is%20as%20defined%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Finstruments-mechanisms%2Finstruments%2Finternational-convention-protection-all-persons-enforced%5C%22%3EInternational%20Convention%20for%20the%20Protection%20of%20All%20Persons%20from%20Enforced%20Disappearance%3C%2Fa%3E%20(2006)%20and%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Finstruments-mechanisms%2Finstruments%2Fdeclaration-protection-all-persons-enforced-disappearance%5C%22%3EUnited%20Nations%20Declaration%20on%20the%20Protection%20of%20All%20Persons%20from%20Enforced%20Disappearance%3C%2Fa%3E%20(A%2FRES%2F47%2F133).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBeyond%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20is%20a%20real%20and%20imminent%20danger%20that%20the%20abductees%20will%20be%20tortured%2C%20raped%20and%20murdered%2C%20and%20notwithstanding%20talk%20of%20a%20Qatar-mediated%20deal%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhamas-israel-prisoners-mustafa-barghouthi-karan-thapar%5C%22%3Eswap%20hostages%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Palestinians%20in%20Israeli%20jails%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20real%20fear%20that%20Hamas%20will%20hand%20over%20the%20Israeli%20abductees%20to%20other%20Palestinian%20militant%20organisations.%20Hamas%20has%20already%20announced%20that%2030%20of%20them%20have%20been%20handed%20to%20the%20Islamic%20Jihad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20clock%20is%20ticking.%20Disappearances%20may%20become%20irreversible.%20For%20example%2C%20some%20of%20the%20elderly%20could%20die%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20medication%2C%20some%20of%20the%20women%20due%20to%20physical%20and%20sexual%20assault.%20The%20history%20of%20abductions%20in%20Chile%20and%20elsewhere%20shows%20that%20Hamas%20may%20deny%20their%20abduction%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20being%20responsible%20for%20their%20fate.%20There%20is%20already%20a%20discrepancy%20between%20the%20number%20of%20abductees%20that%20Hamas%20has%20admitted%20to%20be%20holding%20and%20the%20number%20of%20missing%20persons%20whose%20bodies%20are%20still%20not%20found%20at%20the%20places%20of%20the%20massacre.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPreventing%20enforced%20disappearances%20and%20finding%20the%20disappeared%20is%20not%20only%20an%20international%20duty%20but%20also%20a%20human%20and%20moral%20duty.%20Not%20knowing%20the%20fate%20of%20a%20loved%20one%20and%20the%20inability%20to%20receive%20him%20or%20her%20back%20alive%20or%20bring%20them%20to%20burial%20prevents%20the%20human%20possibility%20of%20their%20family%20for%20personal%20closure%20and%20to%20try%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20the%20disaster%20that%20happened.%20As%20long%20as%20the%20person%20continues%20to%20be%20with%20the%20status%20of%20disappeared%2C%20there%20is%20always%20hope%2C%20even%20after%20many%20years%2C%20in%20defiance%20of%20logic%2C%20that%20the%20person%20might%20return%2C%20which%20also%20prevents%20the%20family%20from%20moving%20on%20and%20rehabilitating%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20believe%20that%20there%20are%20enough%20people%20in%20the%20world%20who%20are%20unable%20to%20justify%20in%20any%20way%20the%20kidnapping%20and%20enforced%20disappearance%20of%20people%20regardless%20of%20the%20national%20origin%20of%20the%20victims.%20We%20call%20on%20them%20to%20raise%20their%20voice%20and%20to%20ask%20their%20governments%20to%20demand%20from%20Hamas%20the%20immediate%20freeing%20of%20all%20the%20Israeli%20and%20non-Israeli%20civilians%20who%20were%20kidnapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDaniel%20Silberman%20Abarzua%2C%20is%20an%20Israeli%20human%20rights%20activist%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FManito-muerta-Relatos-dictadura-Spanish-ebook%2Fdp%2FB0BT8D62JD%2Fref%3Dsr_1_1%3Fqid%3D1696953183%26refinements%3Dp_27%3ADaniel%2BSilberman%2BAbarzua%26s%3Ddigital-text%26sr%3D1-1%5C%22%3Eauthor%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20Father%20David%20Silberman%20Gurovich%20was%20kidnapped%20on%20October%204%2C%201974%20and%20since%20then%20considered%20disappeared.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEitay%20Mack%20is%20an%20Israeli%20human%20rights%20lawyer%20and%20activist%20who%20represented%20Palestinians%20whose%20rights%20were%20violated%20by%20Israel%20and%20also%20families%20of%20the%20disapp