20Private%20Co%3A%20IAS%20Officer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12125951%2FF76OrBQbIAAaSSf.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20administration%20headed%20by%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20went%20against%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20finance%20and%20law%20departments%20and%20amended%20a%20multi-crore%20contract%20midway%20to%20favour%20a%20private%20insurance%20company%2C%20a%20letter%20by%20an%20IAS%20officer%20has%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20contract%20was%20signed%20between%20the%20State%20Health%20Agency%20(SHA)%2C%20the%20nodal%20department%20involved%20in%20rolling%20out%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri-Jan%20Arogya%20Yojna%20(PM-JAY)%20insurance%20scheme%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20Bajaj%20Allianz%20General%20Insurance%20Company%2C%20on%20December%2026%2C%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20day%20later%2C%20on%20December%2027%2C%202020%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20Chief%20Secretary%20Dr%20Arun%20K.%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Lakshya%20Mehta%2C%20was%20hired%20by%20the%20insurance%20company%20where%20he%20currently%20serves%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Senior%20Executive%E2%80%99%2C%20according%20to%20his%20LinkedIn%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20insurance%20company%20sought%20to%20pull%20out%20of%20the%20contract%20in%20September%20next%20year%2C%20the%20SHA%20modified%20the%20contract%20by%20providing%20a%2015%25%20addendum%20to%20the%20existing%20policy%20without%20any%20legal%20backing.%20The%20%E2%80%98illegal%E2%80%99%20changes%20were%20regularised%20by%20the%20Administrative%20Council%20headed%20by%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Sinha%2C%20even%20though%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20finance%20and%20law%20departments%20objected%20to%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20an%20activist%20flagged%20these%20alleged%20irregularities%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigations%2C%20the%20agency%20transferred%20the%20complaint%20after%20six%20months%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Anti-Corruption%20Bureau%20(ACB)%20whose%20director%20reports%20to%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%20one%20of%20the%20alleged%20suspects%20in%20the%20purported%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20claims%20are%20part%20of%20a%20letter%20by%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Public%20Enterprises%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20and%201992%20IAS%20officer%2C%20Ashok%20Kumar%20Parmar%2C%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigations.%20The%20letter%20seeks%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdeeper%20probe%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Insurance%20Regulatory%20and%20Development%20Authority%20of%20India%20(IRDA)%20and%20the%20CBI%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-top-ias-officer-ashok-kumar-parmar-cbi-probe-jal-jeevan-mission%5C%22%3EJ%26amp%3BK%3A%20Why%20a%20Top%20IAS%20Officer%20Has%20Sought%20a%20CBI%20Probe%20Into%20the%20Flagship%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParmar%2C%20who%20previously%20flagged%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%2C%20a%20centrally-sponsored%20scheme%2C%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20has%20also%20sought%20protection%20under%20the%20Whistleblowers%20Protection%20Act%2C%202014%20in%20his%20latest%20letter%20which%20is%20also%20marked%20to%20the%20Principal%20Secretary%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20PMO%2C%20Cabinet%20Secretary%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20and%20Chairman%2C%20IRDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20Yatish%20Yadav%2C%20the%20Media%20Advisor%20to%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%20and%20also%20Chief%20Secretary%20Mehta%2C%20on%20the%20allegations%20of%20%E2%80%9Cabuse%20of%20official%20position%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20acts%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cconfer%20undue%20benefit%E2%80%9D%20on%20a%20private%20firm%20linked%20to%20Mehta.%20This%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20as%20and%20when%20their%20responses%20are%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20top%20government%20official%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20named%20said%20the%20government%20will%20hold%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20spokesperson%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20PM-JAY%20insurance%20scheme%20is%20fully%20funded%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20Ladakh%20while%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20local%20administration%20provides%2010%25%20funding%20support%20while%20the%20rest%20is%20borne%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Parmar%E2%80%99s%20letter%2C%20the%20State%20Health%20Agency%20(SHA)%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20Bajaj%20Allianz%20signed%20the%20three-year%20contract%20on%20December%2025%2C%202020%2C%20with%20a%20provision%20of%20annual%20review%20after%20two%20years%2C%20according%20to%20official%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EClause%209(A)%20of%20the%20contract%2C%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20three%20year%20term%20of%20this%20insurance%20contract%20is%20subject%20to%20renewal%20after%20two%20years%20for%20one%20more%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202021%2C%20less%20than%20a%20year%20after%20the%20contract%20came%20into%20force%2C%20Bajaj%20Allianz%20sought%20to%20withdraw%2C%20reportedly%20citing%20losses.%20A%20top%20official%20of%20the%20administration%2C%20who%20is%20privy%20to%20the%20matter%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20insurance%20company%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20contract%20unless%20the%20SHA%20agreed%20in%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20SHA%20never%20agreed%20to%20the%20plea%20in%20writing.%20Instead%2C%20it%20changed%20the%20contract%20into%20a%20full%20reimbursement%20contract%20on%20December%2025%2C%202021%20with%20a%20top%20up%20fee%20of%2015%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20said%2C%20underlining%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20original%20contract%20happened%20as%20a%20part%20of%20tendering%20process%2C%20but%20the%20addendum%20was%20arbitrary.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInsurance%20companies%20cannot%20claim%20that%20they%20are%20running%20into%20a%20loss%20due%20to%20a%20particular%20insurance%20policy%20for%20J%26amp%3BK%20as%20that%20is%20what%20insurance%20is%20all%20about.%20Diversification%20leads%20to%20its%20viability.%20These%20claims%20and%20the%20SHA%20agreement%20in%20this%20particular%20contract%20has%20no%20basis%20in%20the%20insurance%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20added%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20number%20of%20families%20was%20also%20%E2%80%9Cincreased%20by%201%2C087%2C108%20to%20provide%20more%20financial%20benefit%E2%80%9D%20to%20Bajaj%20Allianz.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20scam%20happened%20between%20December%202021%20and%20April%202022%2C%20as%20per%20the%20modified%20agreement%2C%20and%20it%20has%20caused%20losses%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%20500%20crore%20to%20the%20state%20exchequer%2C%20according%20to%20Parmar%E2%80%99s%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20J%26amp%3BK%20government%20order%20(No.%2049-JK(GAD)%20of%202019%20Dated%3A%2019-11-2019)%2C%20fund%20authorisation%20in%20central%20and%20state%20schemes%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20having%20financial%20implication%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%2050%20crore%20need%20the%20approval%20of%20Chief%20Secretary%20Mehta.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20notification%20dated%20January%209%2C%202020%2C%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20finance%20department%20states%20that%20projects%20above%20Rs%2020%20crore%20shall%20be%20green-lighted%20after%20the%20approval%20of%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Sinha.%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20the%20offices%20have%20to%20be%20in%20the%20loop%20on%20the%20matter.%20It%20is%20either%20pure%20incompetence%20or%20a%20criminal%20nexus%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20quoted%20above%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20top%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20official%2C%20rejecting%20the%20claims%20made%20by%20Parmar%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20said%20that%20the%20policy%20was%20modified%20midway%20because%20Bajaj%20Allianz%20%E2%80%9Crefused%20to%20renew%E2%80%9D%20the%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNew%20contract%20would%20have%20taken%20perhaps%20three%20more%20months%20to%20finalise.%20During%20the%20intermediate%20period%2C%20an%20arrangement%20was%20made%20by%20the%20Health%20department%20as%20per%20General%20Finance%20Rules%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20said%2C%20asking%20not%20to%20be%20quoted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20point%20to%20the%20rules%20under%20which%20the%20contract%20was%20modified%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20choice%20was%20between%20continuity%20of%20service%20or%20disruption.%20Calculations%20made%20by%20the%20health%20department%20show%20that%20the%20model%20they%20adopted%20(to%20provide%2015%25%20extra%20charge%20to%20Bajaj%20Allianz%20was%20least%20costly%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697096018000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12125951%2FF76OrBQbIAAaSSf.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanoj-sinha-jammu-kashmir-bajaj-allianze-pmjay%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ashok%20Kumar%20Parmar%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigations%20seeking%20a%20'deeper%20probe'%20by%20the%20Insurance%20Regulatory%20and%20Development%20Authority%20of%20India%20and%20the%20CBI%20into%20the%20matter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanoj-sinha-jammu-kashmir-bajaj-allianze-pmjay%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Licence%20of%20Company%20Whose%20Cough%20Syrups%20Were%20Linked%20to%20Deaths%20of%20Uzbek%20Kids%20Remains%20Cancelled%3A%20Officials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F25160810%2Fpexels-cottonbro-studio-5858832.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20officials%20associated%20with%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20state%20drug%20control%20administration%20say%20the%20manufacturing%20licence%20of%20Marion%20Biotech%2C%20a%20Noida-based%20pharma%20firm%20whose%20cough%20syrup%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20deaths%20of%20more%20than%2060%20children%20in%20Uzbekistan%20last%20year%2C%20continues%20to%20remain%20cancelled%20as%20of%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20licence%20of%20the%20company%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fuzbekistan-cough-syrup-noida-marion-biotech-mandaviya%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecancelled%20on%20December%2030%2C%202022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20as%20the%20Uzbekistan%20government%20found%20that%20Marion%20Biotech%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fspan%3E%20samples%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fwho-uzbekistan-cough-syrup-noida-product-alert%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Dok1%20Max%20syrup%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Ambronol%20cough%20syrup%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20were%20contaminated%20with%20diethylene%20glycol%20(DEG)%20%E2%80%93%20an%20industrial%20solvent%20that%20is%20used%20as%20an%20antifreeze%20agent.%20According%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews%2Fitem%2F23-01-2023-who-urges-action-to-protect-children-from-contaminated-medicines%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWorld%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20can%20be%20fatal%20even%20if%20consumed%20in%20small%20amounts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20late%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20October%2011%2C%20Noida%20drug%20inspector%20Vaibhav%20Babbar%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20company%E2%80%99s%20plant%20is%20not%20opened%20yet%20as%20the%20%5Blicence%5D%20cancellation%20order%20prevails.%E2%80%9D%20Asked%20again%2C%20he%20reiterated%20that%20the%20order%20%E2%80%9Csustains%20as%20of%20now%20and%20there%20is%20no%20ambiguity%20in%20that%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20further%20information%2C%20he%20redirected%20this%20correspondent%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20head%20of%20drug%20control%20administration%2C%20Shashi%20Mohan%20Gupta.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20company%20has%20not%20even%20submitted%20the%20corrective%20and%20preventive%20actions%20(CAPA)%20plan.%20So%20how%20can%20we%20even%20think%20of%20deliberating%20on%20revoking%20the%20cancellation%20order%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findia-allows-cough-syrup-firm-linked-uzbek-deaths-re-open-factory-document-2023-10-11%2F%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20on%20September%2014%2C%20Gupta%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20no%20known%20case%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20quality%20in%20other%20medicines%20manufactured%20by%20the%20firm.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20in%20view%20of%20natural%20justice%2C%20the%20appeal%20of%20the%20manufacturing%20firm%20is%20partially%20accepted.%20Its%20permission%20to%20make%20products%20using%20(cough%20syrup%20ingredient)%20propylene%20glycol%20is%20cancelled%2C%20and%20it%20is%20allowed%20to%20make%20and%20sell%20all%20other%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20Reuters%20quoted%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20September%20statement%20as%20saying%2C%20on%20October%2011.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Findia-drug-impurities-fight%5C%22%3EInside%20the%20Fight%20To%20Decide%20How%20Pure%20India%E2%80%99s%20Drugs%20Need%20To%20Be%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20talking%20to%20The%20Wire%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20he%20did%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20statement%2C%20but%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20licence%20of%20the%20entire%20plant%20remains%20cancelled%20%5Band%20as%20such%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20manufacture%20%3Cem%3Eany%3C%2Fem%3E%20drug%5D%20and%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20deliberated%20anything%20upon%20its%20reopening%20since%20the%20CAPA%20plan%20has%20not%20been%20submitted%20by%20the%20company%2C%20yet.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20CAPA%20plan%20is%20sent%20%5Bto%20us%5D%2C%20it%20would%20be%20forwarded%20to%20the%20Drug%20Controller%20General%20of%20India%2C%20Rajeev%20Raghuvanshi%2C%20for%20evaluation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%20Gupta%20also%20told%20Reuters%20on%20October%2011%20that%20Raghuvanshi%20had%20asked%20the%20company%20to%20submit%20the%20said%20plan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECAPA%20is%20a%20set%20of%20guidelines%20that%20a%20pharma%20firm%20commits%20to%20following%20once%20it%20has%20been%20found%20violating%20good%20manufacturing%20practices%20in%20an%20investigation%20carried%20out%20by%20drug%20regulatory%20authorities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20said%20plan%2C%20the%20company%20lists%20out%20the%20series%20of%20steps%20it%20would%20undertake%20to%20avoid%20repeating%20the%20violations.%20Once%20the%20plan%20is%20submitted%20to%20the%20regulatory%20authorities%2C%20they%20evaluate%20it%20and%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20its%20suitability%2C%20accordingly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20March%202023%2C%20three%20people%20associated%20with%20the%20firm%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fuzbekistan-child-deaths-three-of-noida-based-firm-arrested-for-contaminated-medicines%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Earrested%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eby%20the%20Noida%20police%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20investigation%20done%20by%20drug%20control%20authorities.%20Marion%20Biotech%E2%80%99s%20owner%20was%20also%20named%20in%20the%20FIR.%20Asked%20about%20his%20status%2C%20the%20UP%20drug%20controller%20said%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20far%20as%20my%C2%A0%20limited%20knowledge%20goes%2C%20he%20got%20a%20stay%20%5Bon%20arrest%5D%20from%20a%20court.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20may%20be%20mentioned%20here%20that%20while%20the%20WHO%20had%20linked%20drugs%20of%20several%20companies%20based%20in%20India%20with%20deaths%20of%20children%20due%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20DEG%20in%20their%20respective%20products%2C%20it%20was%20only%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Marion%20Biotech%20that%20the%20government%20of%20India%20was%20also%20able%20to%20establish%20the%20contamination%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20lab%20investigations.%20In%20no%20other%20such%20instance%20did%20the%20investigation%20in%20India%20establish%20the%20contamination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fwith-officials-rarely-checking-for-impurities-indias-drug-testing-has-a-big-blind-spot%5C%22%3EWith%20Officials%20Rarely%20Checking%20for%20Impurities%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20Drug%20Testing%20Has%20a%20Big%20Blind%20Spot%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUsually%2C%20DEG%20ends%20up%20entering%20these%20drugs%20through%20an%20ingredient%20called%20propylene%20glycol%20(PG)%2C%20which%20is%20added%20to%20syrups%20to%20make%20them%20soluble.%20However%2C%20either%20due%20to%20oversight%2C%20or%20to%20cut%20costs%2C%20pharma%20companies%20end%20up%20using%20PG-mixed%20DG.%20In%20case%20of%20oversight%2C%20they%20often%20don%E2%80%99t%20test%20PG%20for%20any%20impurities%2C%20before%20production%20%E2%80%93%20which%20they%20are%20supposed%20to.%20In%20an%20earlier%20instance%2C%20Marion%20Biotech%E2%80%99s%20Tuhin%20Bhattacharya%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Finvestigates%2Fspecial-report%2Fhealth-coughsyrup-india%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EReuters%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20his%20firms%20had%20sold%20drugs%20without%20checking%20PG%20for%20impurities%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697095773000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F25160810%2Fpexels-cottonbro-studio-5858832.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fmarion-biotech-licence-cough-syrup-uzbek-kids-remains-cancelled%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20report%20had%20said%20that%20barring%20cough%20syrups%2C%20Marion%20Biotech%20would%20be%20allowed%20to%20manufacture%20other%20products%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0provided%20it%20submitted%20the%20corrective%20and%20preventive%20actions%20plan.%20The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20state%20drug%20controller%20told%20The%20Wire%20that%20the%20company%20has%20not%20yet%20submitted%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fmarion-biotech-licence-cough-syrup-uzbek-kids-remains-cancelled%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%E2%80%99s%20Autonomy%20Over%20Body%20vs%20Right%20to%20Life%20of%20Unborn%20Child%3A%20SC%E2%80%99s%20Split%20Judgment%20Decoded%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12115952%2FCambios_en_una_adolescente.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20division%20bench%20comprising%20Justices%20Hima%20Kohli%20and%20B.V.%20Nagarathna%20heard%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcentre-seeks-recall-of-scs-order-permitting-married-woman-to-terminate-26-week-pregnancy%5C%22%3Eapplication%20for%20recall%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20its%20October%2010%20order%20directing%20the%20termination%20of%20the%20pregnancy%20of%20a%20married%20woman%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20October%2011.%20The%20bench%2C%20however%2C%20put%20on%20record%20the%20split%20among%20the%20two%20judges%20on%20whether%20the%20woman%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20seek%20termination%20of%20her%20pregnancy%20could%20be%20recognised%20in%20the%2027th%20week%20of%20gestation.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kohli%20observed%20that%20her%20judicial%20conscience%20could%20not%20permit%20ending%20the%20life%20of%20the%20unborn%20child%2C%20whose%20delivery%20was%20found%20viable%20by%20the%20Medical%20Board%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(AIIMS)%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kohli%20was%20persuaded%20by%20the%20additional%20solicitor%20general%20Aishwarya%20Bhati%2C%20who%20submitted%20that%20the%20bench%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20ought%20not%20to%20be%20concerned%20about%20the%20future%20of%20the%20child%2C%20if%20born%20alive%2C%20but%20should%20only%20decide%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20the%20petitioner-mother%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20terminate%20her%20pregnancy%20in%20the%2027th%20week%20could%20be%20recognised.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20email%20sent%20by%20one%20of%20the%20doctors%20on%20the%20AIIMS%20Medical%20Board%20pointed%20out%20that%20if%20the%20pregnancy%20is%20to%20be%20terminated%20as%20ordered%20by%20the%20court%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20child%20might%20be%20born%20alive%2C%20but%20with%20the%20risk%20of%20severe%20physical%20or%20mental%20disability.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Justice%20Kohli%20expressed%20her%20disappointment%20that%20the%20doctor%20concerned%20did%20not%20share%20her%20opinion%20ahead%20of%20the%20bench%E2%80%99s%20Tuesday%20order%20directing%20the%20termination%20of%20the%20pregnancy%2C%20she%20was%20inclined%20to%20consider%20it%20in%20order%20to%20recall%20that%20order%2C%20as%20sought%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20the%20bench%20to%20talk%20afresh%20to%20the%20petitioner-woman%2C%20who%20was%20present%20in%20the%20court%20during%20the%20hearing%20on%20Wednesday.%20Although%20she%20had%20submitted%20an%20affidavit%20saying%20she%20was%20not%20inclined%20to%20continue%20the%20pregnancy%2C%20the%20bench%20confronted%20her%20with%20the%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20opinion%20and%20sought%20to%20know%20whether%20she%20could%20carry%20the%20pregnancy%20for%20one%20or%20two%20more%20weeks%2C%20if%20it%20ensured%20the%20delivery%20of%20a%20healthy%20child.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20her%20husband%20was%20agreeable%20to%20continue%20with%20the%20pregnancy%20for%20one%20or%20two%20more%20weeks%20as%20recommended%20by%20the%20doctor%2C%20the%20petitioner-woman%20clearly%20refused%20to%20do%20so%2C%20and%20this%20convinced%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20that%20her%20right%20over%20her%20body%20must%20be%20respected%20at%20all%20costs.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBhati%2C%20however%2C%20told%20the%20bench%20that%20the%20woman%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20privacy%20and%20bodily%20autonomy%20ends%20the%20moment%20the%20delivery%20of%20a%20healthy%20child%20is%20found%20viable%20by%20the%20doctors.%20She%20also%20disclosed%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20readiness%20to%20take%20the%20responsibility%20of%20rearing%20the%20child%2C%20as%20the%20petitioner-mother%20was%20not%20inclined%20to%20do%20so%20because%20of%20the%20limitations%20of%20her%20mental%20health%20and%20of%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20financial%20means%20to%20support%20another%20child.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20woman%20had%20told%20the%20court%20that%20she%20was%20suffering%20from%20lactational%20amenorrhea%20(which%20causes%20a%20temporary%20absence%20of%20menstruation%20in%20lactating%20mothers)%20and%20post-partum%20depression%20(a%20medical%20condition%20that%20many%20women%20experience%20after%20having%20a%20baby%2C%20with%20feelings%20of%20sadness%2C%20anxiety%20and%20tiredness).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Nagarathna%2C%20however%2C%20pointed%20to%20the%20petitioner%E2%80%99s%20unwillingness%20to%20continue%20the%20pregnancy%2C%20even%20in%20the%20event%20of%20the%20state%20coming%20forward%20to%20rear%20the%20child%20through%20its%20adoption%20agency.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20while%20Justice%20Kohli%20accepted%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20recall%20application%20of%20the%20bench%E2%80%99s%20previous%20order%2C%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20dismissed%20it.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Nagarathna%20also%20expressed%20her%20disappointment%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20mentioned%20the%20recall%20application%20before%20the%20bench%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20after%20the%20hearing%20in%20his%20court%20was%20over%20at%204%20pm%20on%20Tuesday.%20She%20termed%20it%20as%20an%20intra-court%20appeal%2C%20which%20could%20set%20a%20poor%20legal%20precedent%20within%20the%20court.%20Bhati%2C%20however%2C%20apologised%20for%20her%20conduct%2C%20as%20she%20claimed%20she%20could%20not%20mention%20it%20before%20the%20same%20bench%20on%20Tuesday%20because%20she%20was%20arguing%20another%20case%20before%20another%20bench.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20immediate%20precedent%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20delay%20caused%20by%20Wednesday%E2%80%99s%20split%20among%20the%20judges%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20of%20concern%20to%20the%20petitioner%2C%20the%20immediate%20precedent%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20court%20in%20another%20case%20could%20have%20been%20followed%20by%20the%20Kohli-Nagarathna%20bench%20in%20this%20case%20as%20well.%20But%20that%20was%20not%20considered%20during%20the%20hearing.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ci%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fpdf_upload%2F680-xyz-v-state-of-gujarat-21-aug-2023-490042.pdf%5C%22%3EXYZ%20vs%20State%20of%20Gujarat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Ethe%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Nagarathna%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20had%20on%20August%2021%20held%20that%20a%20woman%20alone%20has%20the%20right%20over%20her%20body%20and%20is%20the%20ultimate%20decision-maker%20on%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20she%20wants%20to%20undergo%20an%20abortion.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20the%20report%20of%20the%20medical%20board%2C%20constituted%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20high%20court%2C%20had%20stated%20that%20although%20there%20is%20no%20congenital%20abnormality%20in%20the%20foetus%2C%20the%20medical%20termination%20of%20the%20pregnancy%20could%20only%20be%20done%20if%20the%20court%20permits%2C%20after%20taking%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20appellant%20and%20explaining%20potential%20risk%20to%20maternal%20health.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20noted%20that%20the%20rape%20survivor%20in%20this%20case%20was%20clinically%20fit%20for%20the%20termination%20procedure%20and%20the%20MTP%20would%20not%20adversely%20affect%20child-bearing%20capacity%20and%20her%20general%20health%20in%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20in%20the%20present%20case%2C%20in%3Ci%3E%C2%A0XYZ%20vs%20State%20of%20Gujarat%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20the%20age%20of%20the%20foetus%20was%20almost%2027%20weeks%20when%20the%20court%20examined%20the%20plea%20for%20termination%20of%20pregnancy.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgain%20as%20in%20the%20present%20case%2C%20the%20likelihood%20of%20adverse%20impact%20of%20the%20continuance%20of%20the%20pregnancy%20on%20the%20mother%E2%80%99s%20mental%20health%20was%20considered%20a%20relevant%20factor%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20It%20may%20be%20argued%20that%20in%20%3Cem%3EXYZ%20vs%20State%20of%20Gujarat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20adverse%20impact%20on%20the%20mental%20health%20of%20the%20mother%20was%20anticipated%20because%20she%20was%20a%20rape%20survivor%20and%20the%20court%20considered%20the%20resultant%20trauma.%20In%20the%20present%20case%2C%20however%2C%20to%20Justice%20Nagarathna%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20petitioner%20is%20a%20married%20woman%2C%20and%20it%20is%20a%20case%20of%20voluntary%20pregnancy%2C%20did%20not%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20her%20conclusion%20that%20there%20was%20a%20risk%20of%20adverse%20impact%20on%20her%20mental%20health%20if%20the%20pregnancy%20continued%20beyond%2027%20weeks.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kohli%2C%20on%20the%20contrary%2C%20was%20persuaded%20by%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20contention%20that%20permitting%20the%20MTP%20of%20a%20married%20woman%20beyond%2027%20weeks%20%E2%80%93%20when%20the%20delivery%20of%20a%20healthy%20child%20is%20found%20viable%20by%20the%20doctors%20%E2%80%93%20may%20set%20a%20wrong%20precedent%20and%20that%20there%20may%20be%20others%20who%20could%20exploit%20it%20and%20seek%20MTP%20beyond%2027%20weeks%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20the%20mother%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cmental%20health%20concerns%E2%80%9D%2C%20notwithstanding%20the%20possibility%20of%20giving%20away%20the%20child%20for%20adoption.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20the%20new%20bench%20would%20deal%20with%20these%20delicate%20issues%20would%20be%20interesting%20to%20watch.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697094949000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12115952%2FCambios_en_una_adolescente.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwoman-autonomy-body-vs-right-to-life-unborn-child-supreme-court-split-judgment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Justices%20Hima%20Kohli%20and%20B.V.%20Nagarathna%20split%20on%20a%20married%20woman%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20abort%20her%20pregnancy%20in%20the%2027th%20week%2C%20leaving%20it%20to%20the%20CJI%20to%20constitute%20another%20bench%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwoman-autonomy-body-vs-right-to-life-unborn-child-supreme-court-split-judgment%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Global%20Leadership%20Is%20Not%20Just%20About%20Drafting%20a%20Statement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22165508%2FH20230909138364.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20not%20attending%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20party%20at%20the%20G-20%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20effectively%20signalled%20that%20the%20group%20no%20longer%20matters%20in%20geo-economic%20and%20geo-political%20terms.%20What%20matters%20is%20the%20G-7%20and%20its%20direct%20competitor%20BRICS.%20And%20if%20the%20South%20African%20edition%20of%20BRICS%20is%20the%20sign%20of%20times%20to%20come%2C%20then%20this%20is%20where%20the%20world%20is%20converging.%20However%2C%20to%20convey%20China%E2%80%99s%20core%20message%20to%20the%20world%20that%20it%20favours%20globalisation%2C%20it%20sent%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang%20to%20attend%20the%20G-20%20summit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProtocol%20could%20be%20another%20reason%20why%20Xi%20may%20have%20decided%20to%20miss%20the%20Delhi%20jamboree%20since%20Modi%20would%20have%20given%20exceptional%20attention%20to%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%20Moreover%2C%20to%20communicate%20that%20bilateral%20ties%20were%20at%20an%20all-time%20low%2C%20Xi%20did%20not%20bother%20to%20personally%20convey%20his%20absence%20to%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExcept%20for%20the%20US%2C%20all%20nations%20believe%20that%20the%20world%20is%20moving%20towards%20multipolarity%20with%20two%20overarching%20global%20visions%20led%20by%20the%20US%20and%20China%20respectively.%20Therefore%2C%20so%20long%20as%20they%20are%20not%20pushed%20to%20choose%20between%20the%20two%20visions%2C%20nations%20are%20hopeful%20of%20drawing%20benefits%20from%20both.%20What%20is%20underplayed%20is%20the%20reality%20that%20global%20prosperity%20ultimately%20hinges%20on%20the%20success%20of%20the%20fourth%20industrial%20revolution%20underpinned%20by%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F21222939%2FPresident_Biden_met_with_President_Xi_of_the_PRC_before_the_2022_G20_Bali_Summit.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F21222939%2FPresident_Biden_met_with_President_Xi_of_the_PRC_before_the_2022_G20_Bali_Summit.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F21222939%2FPresident_Biden_met_with_President_Xi_of_the_PRC_before_the_2022_G20_Bali_Summit-300x149.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-659470%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22508%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20shakes%20hands%20with%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G20%20leaders%E2%80%99%20summit%20in%20Bali%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20November%2014%2C%202022.%20Photo%3A%20White%20House%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20Public%20domain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20software%20driven%20revolution%20with%20its%20competing%20standards%2C%20rules%2C%20norms%2C%20and%20regulations%20for%20the%20two%20visions%20will%20compel%20the%20nations%20to%20choose%20between%20them%20for%20digital%20commerce%2C%20trade%2C%20and%20navigation.%20And%20this%20may%20happen%20as%20early%20as%202030.%20In%20geopolitical%20terms%2C%20this%20means%20that%20unless%20the%20US%20endorses%20globalisation%20in%20totality%20(trade%2C%20commerce%2C%20and%20especially%20technology%2C%20which%20is%20unlikely)%2C%20early%20signs%20of%20bipolarity%20fragmented%20between%20the%20two%20visions%20may%20emerge%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20decade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%2C%20which%20is%20a%20key%20geopolitical%20pivot%20in%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20%E2%80%93%20where%20the%20two%20visions%20will%20play%20out%20%E2%80%93%20has%20chosen%20to%20align%20itself%20with%20the%20US%20vision.%20Moreover%2C%20unwilling%20to%20adjust%20with%20the%20risen%20(not%20rising%20or%20emerging)%20China%2C%20India%20has%20picked%20competition%20over%20cooperation%20with%20Beijing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20Asia%20Society%20India%20on%20September%2013%2C%202022%2C%20external%20affairs%20minister%2C%20S.%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20a%20multi-polar%20Asia%20is%20necessary%20for%20the%20Asian%20century%20and%20multi-polar%20world%2C%20implying%20that%20India%20and%20China%20are%20equal%20poles%20in%20Asia%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20251px)%2085vw%2C%20251px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12102237%2F51TTL0Br3L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-196x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22251%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12102237%2F51TTL0Br3L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-196x300.jpg%20196w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12102237%2F51TTL0Br3L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20654w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679616%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22384%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EZbigniew%20Brzezinski%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Grand%20Chessboard%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1997)%20published%20by%20Basic%20Books.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJaishankar%20has%20clearly%20not%20read%20or%20understood%20Zbigniew%20Brzezinski%E2%80%99s%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Grand%20Chessboard%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhich%20is%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Efascinating%20treatise%20on%20global%20strategy.%20According%20to%20Brzezinski%2C%20geo-strategic%20players%20are%20those%20nations%20which%20have%20the%20capability%2C%20capacity%20and%20political%20will%20to%20influence%20events%20beyond%20their%20borders.%20The%20US%2C%20China%2C%20and%20Russia%20fall%20in%20this%20category%20as%20distinct%20from%20major%20powers%20like%20Germany%2C%20France%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Japan%20and%20the%20like.%20Thus%2C%20all%20geostrategic%20powers%20are%20major%20powers%2C%20but%20all%20major%20powers%20are%20not%20geostrategic%20players.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20world%2C%20major%20powers%20should%20be%20assessed%20by%20their%20technological%20prowess%20(as%20the%20fourth%20industrial%20revolution%20builds%20on%20the%20third%20revolution).%20This%20is%20central%20to%20both%20economic%20and%20military%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBased%20on%20power%20in%20the%20field%20of%20technology%20%E2%80%93%20AI%20and%20emerging%20technologies%20which%20converge%20into%20it%20%E2%80%93%20India%20is%20not%20in%20the%20global%20game.%20Yet%2C%20being%20a%20significant%20geopolitical%20pivot%2C%20whose%20importance%20is%20derived%20not%20by%20its%20national%20power%2C%20but%20by%20its%20sensitive%20location%2C%20India%20is%20being%20courted%20by%20all%20three%20geostrategic%20players.%20Besides%20its%20geography%2C%20which%20sits%20astride%20the%203%2C000%20nautical%20miles%20sea%20lanes%20of%20communication%20from%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20to%20the%20Strait%20of%20Malacca%20%E2%80%93%20through%20which%20China%E2%80%99s%20four%20trillion%20dollars%20trade%20passes%20annually%20%E2%80%93%20India%20is%20also%20a%20huge%20market%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20added%20attractions%20for%20the%20US%20are%20India%E2%80%99s%20massive%2C%20disciplined%20military%3B%20it%20being%20the%20biggest%20arms%20importer%20in%20the%20world%3B%20and%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20belief%20that%20a%20tight%20US%20embrace%20will%20help%20it%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20region%20with%20China.%20Before%20discussing%20why%20India%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20as%20it%20is%20evolving%20may%20end%20up%20being%20a%20dangerous%20self-goal%2C%20there%20is%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20two%20global%20visions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETwo%20global%20visions%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20vision%20seeks%20a%20replay%20of%20the%20Cold%20War%20where%20containment%20of%20the%20Soviet%20sphere%20of%20influence%20(politically%20and%20militarily)%20by%20deterrence%2C%20without%20a%20direct%20war%20between%20the%20two%20blocs%2C%20eventually%20led%20to%20the%20USSR%E2%80%99s%20demise%20along%20with%20the%20Warsaw%20Pact%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20US%20created%20the%20Bretton%20Woods%20institutions%20%E2%80%93%20the%20World%20Bank%20and%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20%E2%80%93%20for%20global%20economic%20integration.%20It%20dominated%20the%20world%20by%20its%20exceptional%20military-industrial%20complex%2C%20established%20some%20760%20military%20bases%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20led%20the%20military-technological%20revolution%2C%20and%20ushered%20in%20the%20third%20industrial%20revolution%2C%20pivoted%20on%20chips%20and%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20unipolar%20scenario%2C%20from%201991%20to%202017%2C%20the%20US%20ruled%20the%20world%20based%20on%20its%20military%20and%20dollar%20dominance.%20It%20toppled%20governments%20through%20colour%20revolutions%2C%20wars%2C%20and%20sanctions%20to%20propagate%20a%20hegemony%20that%20sought%20to%20build%20a%20world%20in%20which%20its%20corporations%20and%20military%20would%20have%20full%20freedom.%20Its%20official%20ideology%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20democracy%20and%20human%20rights%2C%20but%20these%20were%20mostly%20expedient%20slogans%20to%20further%20Washington%E2%80%99s%20global%20interests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20as%20the%20US%20was%20fighting%20small%20wars%2C%20especially%20in%20Afghanistan%20and%20Iraq%2C%20by%202010%2C%20it%20realised%20that%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%20could%20match%20the%20US%20military%20in%20the%20west%20Pacific.%20The%20PLA%20had%20operational%20systems%20and%20guided%20munitions%20that%2C%20it%20noted%2C%20were%20as%20capable%20as%20its%20own.%20The%20PLA%20could%20close%20the%20kill%20chain%20as%20quickly%20as%20the%20US%20military.%20It%20could%20also%20conduct%20stand-off%20precision%20attacks%20at%20long%20ranges%20as%20well%20as%20the%20US%20military%20with%20its%20indigenous%20mortars%2C%20rockets%2C%20missiles%2C%20and%20artillery%20projectiles%20most%20of%20which%20were%20guided.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECoupled%20with%20miniaturisation%2C%20guided%20weapons%20brought%20unprecedented%20lethality%20at%20long%20ranges.%20This%20led%20the%20Pentagon%20to%20announce%20the%20third%20offset%20strategy%20driven%20by%20AI%20and%20autonomy%20in%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20China%20announced%20its%20One%20Belt%20One%20Road%20(or%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative)%20project%20in%202013%20followed%20by%20the%20Digital%20Silk%20Road%20in%202015.%20With%20expertise%20in%20destroying%20nations%20but%20none%20in%20building%20them%2C%20the%20US%20was%20at%20sea%20in%20the%20face%20of%20numerous%20challenges%20presented%20by%20China%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EIts%20exceptional%20capability%20and%20capacity%20in%20international%20infrastructure%20building%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3Edeep%20pockets%20to%20fund%20the%20BRI%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3Emilitary%20capability%20in%20the%20domains%20of%20space%2C%20cyber%2C%20and%20electromagnetic%20spectrum%2C%20and%20land-based%20missiles%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3Eits%20intense%20integration%20with%20the%20world%20economy%20whereby%20China%20was%20the%20major%20trading%20partner%20of%20over%20140%20nations%20and%20regions%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3Eit%20being%20the%20largest%20global%20manufacturer%20and%20trader%20in%20goods.%20This%20made%20terms%20like%20decoupling%2C%20de-risking%2C%20and%20diversifying%20difficult%20to%20carry%20through%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3Eits%20exceptional%20civil-military%20fusion%20for%20developing%20AI%20ecosystem%2C%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3Eits%20ability%20to%20commercialise%20AI%20incubated%20in%20the%20US%20(Silicon%20Valley).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20AI%20is%20built%20and%20not%20bought%20off%20the%20shelf%2C%20China%2C%20by%202017%2C%20could%20lead%20the%20US%20in%20three%20of%20the%20six%20stacks%20which%20comprise%20AI.%20While%20lagging%20behind%20the%20US%20in%20AI%20hardware%2C%20software%2C%20and%20human%20resources%2C%20China%20excelled%20in%20data%20management%2C%20applications%20(for%20commercialisation)%2C%20and%20integration%20or%20Internet%20of%20Things%20(IoT%2C%20also%20called%20internet%20modules).%20This%20started%20a%20tech%20war%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration%20banning%20Huawei%205G%20in%202018%20followed%20by%20denial%20of%C2%A0%20chips%2C%20chip-making%20design%20software%20and%20tools%20to%20China%20by%20the%20Biden%20administration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12102642%2Fbri_map.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12102642%2Fbri_map.png%20780w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12102642%2Fbri_map-300x169.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679620%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBelt%20and%20Road%20Initiative.%20Photo%3A%20World%20Bank%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnable%20to%20match%20China%E2%80%99s%20BRI%2C%20the%20US%20started%20maligning%20it%20by%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%98debt%20trap%E2%80%99%2C%20underplaying%20the%20fact%20that%20138%20nations%20from%20the%20Global%20South%20were%20on%20board.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20US%20with%20its%20G7%20partners%20also%20dabbled%20in%20half-baked%20connectivity%20projects%20like%20Build-Back-Better-World%2C%20Global%20Gateway%2C%20and%20recently%20the%20Indian-Middle%20East-Europe%20project%20unveiled%20at%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20India.%20These%20projects%2C%20if%20they%20ever%20fructify%2C%20will%20likely%20supplement%20the%20BRI%20rather%20than%20challenge%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20decided%20to%20double%20down%20on%20its%20own%20strength%20by%20turning%20the%20Obama%20administration%E2%80%99s%202011%20%E2%80%98pivot%20to%20Asia%E2%80%99%20policy%20into%20%E2%80%98integrated%20deterrence%E2%80%99%20by%20aligning%20allies%2C%20strategic%20partners%20(India)%20and%20the%20Atlantic-specific%20NATO%20into%20its%20Indo-Pacific%20defence%20network.%20It%20was%20lost%20on%20the%20US%20that%20there%20is%20no%20military%20answer%20to%20the%20BRI%3A%20a%20strategy%20built%20on%20expansion%20of%20commerce%2C%20trade%20and%20navigation%20by%20connectivity%2C%20AI%2C%20and%20big%20data.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20US%20continues%20to%20be%20driven%20by%20containment%20and%20global%20domination%2C%20China%20speaks%20about%20%E2%80%98global%20respect%E2%80%99.%20It%20asks%20that%20nations%20onboard%20the%20BRI%20framework%20%E2%80%93%20which%20includes%20the%20SCO%20and%20the%20Russia-led%20Eurasian%20Economic%20Union%20nations%20%E2%80%93%20remain%20sensitive%20to%20China%E2%80%99s%20interests%20while%20framing%20their%20foreign%20policy.%20To%20achieve%20this%20vision%2C%20China%20has%20enunciated%20what%20it%20terms%20its%20Global%20Development%20Initiative%20(GDI)%2C%20Global%20Security%20Initiative%20(GSI)%2C%20and%20Global%20Civilisation%20Initiative%20(GCI)%20concepts%2C%20working%20under%20the%20United%20Nations%20umbrella.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAligned%20with%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs)%20for%202030%2C%20GDI%20is%20expected%20to%20create%20green%2C%20efficient%2C%20and%20cost-effective%20development%20given%20China%E2%80%99s%20lead%20in%20Lithium-ion%20batteries%2C%20solar%20batteries%2C%20and%20new%20energy%20vehicles%20through%20BRI%20which%20will%20offer%20a%20mix%20of%20physical%2C%20mobile%2C%20and%20digital%20economies%20to%20the%20Global%20South%20nations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mobile%20economy%2C%20whose%20inflection%20point%20in%20China%20came%20in%202014%2C%20is%20about%20mobile%20internet%2C%204G%20networks%20with%20consumers%20in%20the%20lead.%20This%20mobile%20economy%20with%20imported%20hardware%20was%20offered%20to%20the%20world%20recently%20by%20India%20as%20a%20highpoint%20of%20its%20G-20%20presidency.%20Moreover%2C%20since%20China%20has%20a%20lead%20over%20the%20G7%20nations%20in%20rolling%20out%20a%205G%20network%2C%20the%20inflection%20point%20for%20a%20digital%20economy%20based%20on%20AI%2C%20data%2C%20cloud%2C%20and%20blockchain%20came%20in%202017%20in%20China.%20The%20digital%20economy%20led%20by%20enterprises%20is%20about%20the%20industrial%20internet%20where%2C%20given%20China%E2%80%99s%20expertise%20in%20software%2C%20it%20is%20ahead%20in%20the%20internet%20module%20or%20IoT.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFast%20forward%20to%20some%20possible%20scenarios%2C%20three%20to%20five%20years%20from%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELarge%20Language%20Models%20(LLMs)%20like%20Chat%20GPT-4%2C%20which%20took%20the%20world%20by%20storm%20in%202023%20by%20its%20generative%20AI%2C%20will%20be%20hundreds%20of%20times%20larger%20with%20exceptional%20capabilities.%20Instead%20of%20generating%20text%2C%20the%20new%20LLMs%20will%20be%20able%20to%20generate%20sequences%20of%20actions%20to%20be%20done%20and%20then%20be%20able%20to%20do%20them%20by%20itself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20its%20lead%20in%20the%20industrial%20internet%20on%20account%20of%205G%20availability%20at%20scale%2C%20China%20will%20likely%20focus%20its%20LLMs%20not%20on%20Natural%20Language%20Processing%20(NLP)%20to%20generate%20text%2C%20videos%2C%20and%20images%20like%20Chat%20GPT%2C%20but%20on%20the%20SDGs%20underpinning%20the%20GDI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20since%20the%20LLMs%20will%20be%20able%20to%20generate%20AI%20which%20could%20communicate%20and%20negotiate%20with%20humans%20on%20the%20phone%20and%20interact%20with%20other%20AIs%20to%20ensure%20glitches%20in%20supply%20chains%20are%20removed%20quickly%2C%20they%20will%20have%20tremendous%20uses%20in%20health%20services%2C%20smart%20logistics%2C%20smart%20cities%2C%20digital%20finances%2C%20biotechnology%2C%20and%20other%20applications%20of%20the%20fourth%20industrial%20revolution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELLMs%20will%20also%20have%20a%20big%20role%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20metaverse%20or%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20the%20internet.%20The%20convergence%20of%20virtual%20reality%20and%20a%20digital%20second%20life%20(avatars)%20will%20be%20boosted%20by%20generative%20AI%20for%20business%20models%2C%20trade%2C%20and%20commerce.%20Thus%2C%20the%20technology%20layer%20underpinning%20the%20metaverse%20will%20comprise%20AR%2FVR%20(Augmented%20Reality%2FVirtual%20Reality)%2C%20IoT%2C%205G%2C%206G%2C%20and%20mesh%20network%20which%20self-organise%20and%20self-configure%20nodes%20for%20efficiently%20routing%20data%20to%20and%20from%20clients.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-and-china-are-trapped-in-a-conflict-of-their-own-making%5C%22%3EIndia%20and%20China%20are%20Trapped%20in%20a%20Conflict%20of%20Their%20Own%20Making%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20the%20above%2C%20two%20things%20become%20clear%20%E2%80%93%20one%2C%20the%20need%20for%20cyber%20security%20against%20backdoor%20and%20adversarial%20attacks%2C%20and%20second%2C%20to%20set%20standards%2C%20norms%2C%20regulations%2C%20and%20roles%20for%20new%20technologies%20of%20the%20fourth%20industrial%20revolution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20US%20is%20determined%20to%20obstruct%20China%E2%80%99s%20innovations%2C%20the%20tech%20war%20started%20by%20the%20US%20will%20intensify.%20This%20is%20likely%20to%20result%20in%20the%20splintering%20of%20the%20internet%20and%20eventually%20fragmentation%20of%20industrial%20supply%20chains%20for%20trade%20and%20commerce.%20Given%20this%2C%20it%20will%20become%20increasingly%20difficult%20for%20nations%20aligned%20with%20the%20two%20global%20visions%20to%20trade%20with%20one%20another%20digitally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurthermore%2C%20most%20Global%20South%20nations%20have%20been%20attracted%20by%20GSI%20whose%20basic%20premise%20is%20indivisible%20security%2C%20implying%20a%20no%20zero-sum%20game%20or%20one%E2%80%99s%20security%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20another%E2%80%99s%20security.%20Simply%20put%2C%20instead%20of%20absolute%20security%2C%20nations%20should%20consider%20relative%20security.%20GSI%20also%20advocates%20an%20end%20to%20unilateral%20sanctions%20(outside%20the%20UN)%20and%20bloc%20confrontation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20non-interference%20in%20the%20internal%20affairs%20of%20other%20nations.%20It%20also%20advocates%20respect%20for%20each%20nation%E2%80%99s%20traditions%20and%20values%20%E2%80%93%20as%20against%20the%20instrumentalist%20%E2%80%98universal%20values%E2%80%99%20for%20human%20rights%2C%20democracy%2C%20and%20empowerment%20which%2C%20as%20we%20noted%2C%20the%20US%20pursues%20only%20selectively.%20In%20a%20fast-fragmenting%20world%2C%20all%20nations%2C%20especially%20big%20ones%20like%20India%2C%20will%20have%20to%20choose%20a%20side.%20%E2%80%98Balancing%E2%80%99%20may%20no%20longer%20be%20an%20option.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20senior%20Indian%20analysts%E2%80%99%20contention%20that%20India%20should%20remain%20engaged%20with%20BRICS%2C%20the%20SCO%2C%20QUAD%2C%20and%20the%20G-7%20nations%20as%20this%20would%20increase%20its%20diplomatic%20options%20in%20a%20polarised%20world%20is%20not%20sustainable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EG-20%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20presidency%20of%20the%20G-20%20summit%20will%20be%20remembered%20for%20two%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%2C%20whose%20nation%E2%80%99s%20economies%2C%20according%20to%20IMF%202023%20figures%2C%20grew%20faster%20than%20any%20other%20G-7%20nation.%20After%20the%20spectacular%20success%20of%20the%20BRICS%202023%20summit%20in%20Johannesburg%2C%20the%20answer%20to%20US%E2%80%99%20dollar%20dominance%20was%20found%20in%20trading%20in%20local%20currency%20and%20BRICS%20Pay%20(this%20will%20not%20replace%2C%20but%20displace%20SWIFT)%2C%20an%20electronic%20banking%20system%20which%20Iran%20will%20join%20in%20January%202024%20amongst%20other%20nations.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20African%20Union%20as%20the%20new%20G-20%20member%20was%20a%20pyrrhic%20victory%20compared%20with%20the%20six%20new%20members%20added%20to%20the%20BRICS%20(these%20include%20all%20global%20major%20energy%20exporters%20and%20importers)%20given%20that%2050%20of%20the%2054%20African%20nations%20attended%20the%202023%20BRICS%20summit.%20With%20%24300%20billion%20annual%20trade%2C%20China%20is%20the%20largest%20trading%20partner%20of%20the%20African%20continent%20and%20Russia%20is%20the%20biggest%20arms%20exporter.%20Thus%2C%20while%20China%20is%20the%20undisputed%20leader%20of%20Global%20South%2C%20to%20humour%20India%2C%20the%20US%20and%20G-7%20have%20endorsed%20it%20as%20the%20voice%20of%20Global%20South.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F10175233%2FF5pyX8ua4AAoHu2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F10175233%2FF5pyX8ua4AAoHu2.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F10175233%2FF5pyX8ua4AAoHu2-300x97.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F10175233%2FF5pyX8ua4AAoHu2-1024x329.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672418%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22386%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EG20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Sunday%2C%20September%2010.%20Photo%3A%20%40narendramodi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecond%2C%20the%20Delhi%20G-20%20joint%20declaration%20was%20made%20possible%20not%20because%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20foresight%20or%20India%E2%80%99s%20exceptional%20negotiating%20skills%20but%20because%20India%20is%20a%20major%20geopolitical%20pivot%20wooed%20by%20the%20US%2C%20and%20not%20yet%20abandoned%20by%20China%20and%20Russia.%20The%20Delhi%20declaration%20was%20a%20watered-down%20version%20of%20the%20Bali%20G-20%20declaration%20since%20for%20the%20US%2C%20the%20bilateral%20Modi-Biden%20meeting%20before%20the%20official%20G-20%20summit%20was%20far%20more%20important%20that%20the%20joint%20statement%20which%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%20Modi%20had%20one-on-one%20meetings%20with%20most%20G-7%20nations%20since%20they%2C%20like%20the%20US%2C%20have%20stakes%20in%20the%20Indo%20Pacific%20region%20which%20may%20be%20decisive%20factors%20in%20global%20geopolitics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20the%C2%A0%20US%E2%80%99s%20support%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20G-20%2C%20which%20comes%20close%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20general%20election%20in%202024%2C%20it%20would%20be%20natural%20for%20Biden%20to%20want%20a%20quick%20execution%20of%20the%20joint%20declaration%20signed%20during%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20in%20June.%20Washington%20does%20not%20want%20India%20to%20go%20the%20Australia%20way%2C%20which%2C%20while%20being%20a%20member%20of%20both%20QUAD%20and%20AUKUS%2C%20is%20now%20busy%20improving%20its%20trade%20ties%20with%20China%2C%20or%20like%20Malaysia%20which%20has%20decided%20to%20downplay%20China%E2%80%99s%20new%20map%20which%20infringes%20its%20sovereignty%2C%20in%20favour%20of%20improving%20prospects%20for%20trade%20with%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20gambles%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20silence%20on%20China%2C%20despite%20cozying%20up%20to%20the%20US%2C%20will%20have%20its%20limits%20if%20really%20pushed%20to%20the%20brink.%20Ever%20since%20the%20Galwan%20episode%20in%20June%202020%2C%20India%20has%20gone%20quiet%20on%20even%20its%20other%20neighbour%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20with%20it%20not%20making%20its%20usual%20appearance%20in%20election%20rhetoric.%20With%20a%20tendency%20to%20see%20everything%20through%20a%20prism%20of%20its%20domestic%20audience%2C%20China%20and%20Pakistan%20being%20aligned%20poses%20a%20graver%20challenge%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20politics%20than%20is%20acknowledged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20good%20geopolitics%20is%20and%20should%20be%20rooted%20in%20geography%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20statecraft%20should%20concentrate%20on%20decent%20relations%20with%20Pakistan%20and%20China.%20If%20India%20was%20honest%20with%20itself%2C%20it%20would%20know%20that%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20April%202020%20incursions%20into%20Ladakh%20were%C2%A0%20the%20consequence%20of%20India%20creating%20a%20new%20map%20after%20the%20revocation%20of%20Article%20370%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20on%C2%A0%20August%205%2C%202019)%20which%20resulted%20in%20a%C2%A0%20Union%20Territory%20(UT)%20status%20for%20Ladakh.%20Conscious%20of%20this%20fact%2C%20and%20China%E2%80%99s%20displeasure%2C%20external%20affairs%20minister%20Jaishankar%20travelled%20to%20Beijing%20on%20August%2011%2C%202019%20to%20explain%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20new%20map%20would%20not%20change%20the%20reality%20on%20the%20ground.%20China%20rejected%20his%20explanation%20and%20changed%20reality%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESadly%2C%20the%20Indian%20military%20(medium%20power)%20risks%20being%20outflanked%20by%20the%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20(major%20power)%20in%20case%20of%20a%20confrontation%20and%20this%20challenge%20has%20three%20dimensions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%2C%20as%20against%20the%20Indian%20military%2C%20which%20will%20wage%20combat%20across%20physical%20battle%20spaces%20comprising%20land%2C%20air%2C%20and%20sea%20domains%2C%20the%20PLA%20will%20likely%20engage%20four%20battles%20paces.%20Its%20physical%20battle-space%20will%20comprise%20land%2C%20air%2C%20sea%2C%20outer%20space%2C%20and%20near-space%20(for%20hypersonic%20missiles)%20domains.%20The%20virtual%20battle-space%20will%20include%20cyberspace%20and%20the%20electromagnetic%20spectrum.%20The%20information%20battle-space%20will%20have%20wired%20and%20wireless%20networks%20through%20which%20data%20passes.%20And%20the%20cognition%20battle%20space%20%E2%80%93%20where%20an%20information%20war%20will%20be%20unleashed%20%E2%80%93%20will%20involve%20a%20mind%20war%2C%20which%20will%20entail%20assaulting%20the%20enemy%E2%80%99s%20judgement.%20The%20PLA%20is%20likely%20to%20emphasise%20cognitive%20confrontation%20and%20push%20to%20seek%20an%20early%20cognitive%20victory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%2C%20unlike%20the%20Indian%20military%2C%20the%20war%20fought%20by%20the%20PLA%20will%20not%20be%20confined%20to%20a%20battlefield%20or%20combat%20space.%20And%20three%2C%20China%20will%20not%20fight%20a%20tactical%20war%20at%20the%20frontline%20where%20the%20Indian%20army%20has%20an%20advantage%2C%20but%20across%20the%20entire%20combat%20zone%20at%20the%20operational%20level%20where%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20war%20will%20be%20decided.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20all%20this%2C%20never%20has%20it%20been%20more%20critical%20for%20India%20to%20improve%20relations%20with%20its%20neighbour%2C%20China.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20tactics%2C%20but%20about%20being%20on%20the%20right%20side%20of%20history.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPravin%20Sawhney%E2%80%99s%20recent%20book%20is%C2%A0The%20Last%20War%3A%20How%20AI%20Will%20Shape%20India%E2%80%99s%20Final%20Showdown%20With%20China%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697094004000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22165508%2FH20230909138364.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fglobal-leadership-is-not-just-about-drafting-a-statement%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Based%20on%20its%20achievements%20in%20key%20fields%20of%20technology%2C%20India%20is%20not%20in%20the%20global%20game.%20Yet%2C%20a