t%20the%20bodies%20after%20much%20deliberations%20with%20some%20of%20the%20most%20celebrated%20faces%20of%20vigilantism.%20They%20had%20not%20anticipated%20the%20consequences%20of%20the%20thrashing%20and%20panicked.%20They%20could%20see%20both%20dying%2C%20and%20that%20is%20when%20they%20contacted%20the%20vigilantes%20of%20Haryana%20for%20guidance.%20They%20decided%20to%20burn%20the%20bodies%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20forensic%20evidence%20was%20left.%20We%20are%20probing%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20role%20of%20these%20vigilantes%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fharyana%2Finfluential-vigilantes-ordered-burning-of-nasir-junaid-bodies-552526%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fground-report-how-junaid-and-nasir-were-killed-by-cow-vigilantes%5C%22%3EGround%20Report%3A%20How%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir%20Were%20Killed%20by%20%E2%80%98Cow%20Vigilantes%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Multan%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcow-vigilantes-extort-money-from-cattle-smugglers-alleges-key-accused-in-nasir-junaid-murder-case%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cow%20vigilantes%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Rajasthan%20have%20been%20extorting%20money%20from%20cattle%20smugglers%20to%20allow%20them%20safe%20passage%20through%20the%20states.%20These%20vigilantes%20ran%20a%20close-knit%20group%20and%20tracked%20the%20movement%20of%20smugglers%20and%20trucks%20carrying%20cattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMultan%E2%80%99s%20statements%20highlight%20that%20these%20groups%20closely%20monitored%20smuggler%20activities%20and%20demanded%20payments%20from%20them.%20Failure%20to%20pay%20often%20resulted%20in%20violence%20and%20police%20intervention.%20It%20is%20this%20extortion%20money%20that%20helped%20these%20groups%20to%20fund%20their%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CExtortion%20is%20the%20key%20source%20of%20income%20of%20these%20gangs.%20They%20have%20a%20strong%20network%20in%20Mewat.%20They%20have%20lists%20of%20cattle%20smugglers%20and%20seek%20payment%20from%20them%20for%20allowing%20their%20trucks%20to%20pass%20through%20the%20area.%20If%20they%20fail%20to%20pay%2C%20they%20are%20thrashed%20and%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20police%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20went%20on%20to%20add%20that%20the%20payments%20depended%20on%20the%20number%20and%20type%20of%20cattle%20being%20smuggled%20and%20the%20area%20they%20were%20caught.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENasir%20and%20Junaid%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Multhan%2C%20earned%20the%20wrath%20of%20the%20accused%20for%20helping%20smugglers%20pass%20through%20the%20area%20without%20paying%20the%20extortion%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20plan%20of%20the%20accused%20was%20to%20catch%20the%20duo%20red-handed%20and%20then%20hand%20them%20over%20to%20the%20police%2C%20they%20could%20not%20do%20so%20as%20they%20could%20not%20get%20hold%20of%20the%20truck%20smuggling%20cattle.%20It%20was%20then%20the%20accused%20thrashed%20them%2C%20according%20to%20the%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20Multan%20in%20custody%2C%20Rajasthan%20Police%20expect%20him%20to%20reveal%20more%20about%20the%20case%20as%20well%20as%20the%20cow%20vigilantism%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20killing%20of%20the%20duo%20has%20become%20a%20major%20political%20issue%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20which%20is%20going%20to%20polls%20next%20month.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20dominate%20electoral%20discourse%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Mewat%20region%2C%20which%20comprises%20Alwar%2C%20Deeg%2C%20and%20Bharatpur%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20daily%2C%20there%20have%20been%20protests%20in%20the%20region%20against%20Rajasthan%20Police%20handing%20over%20Monu%20Manesar%20to%20Haryana%20Police.%20Manesar%2C%20who%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmonu-manesar-arrested-by-haryana-police-sit%5C%22%3Earrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20in%20connection%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3Eviolence%20in%20Nuh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20Rajasthan%20Police.%20He%20was%20then%20taken%20into%20Haryana%20Police%20custody%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20Police%20is%20also%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20other%20accused%20in%20the%20Nasir-Junaid%20murder%20case.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20hand%20over%20a%20list%20of%20cow%20vigilantes%20to%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697093119000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F16225727%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-02-16-at-8.59.38-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnasir-junaid-burnt-on-the-advice-of-senior-vigilantes-reveals-prime-accused%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20accused%20said%20they%20wanted%20to%20thrash%20the%20duo%20and%20hand%20them%20over%20to%20police%2C%20but%20the%20physical%20assault%20went%20out%20of%20hand%2C%20resulting%20in%20their%20death.%20It%20was%20then%20they%20were%20advised%20by%20vigilantes%20to%20burn%20the%20bodies%20to%20destroy%20evidence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnasir-junaid-burnt-on-the-advice-of-senior-vigilantes-reveals-prime-accused%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shareholders%20Defeat%20Imax%20Bid%20to%20Buy%20up%20China%20Subsidiary%2C%20Shares%20Wobble%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697091971000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2Fwanda-imax-china.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop