20and%20he%20enquired%20about%20it.%20He%20was%20told%20that%20these%20had%20not%20been%20working%20for%20nine%20years%20as%20the%20electricity%20requirements%20could%20not%20be%20met.%20%E2%80%9CI%20got%20six%201.5%20kW%20solar%20panels%20installed%20in%20the%20school%20which%20ensure%20the%20smooth%20functioning%20of%20the%20computers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FScreenshot-2022-07-07-155357_11zon-1696939453.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20solar%20panels%20installed%20in%20the%20school%20are%20now%20used%20to%20power%20the%20computers%20that%20lay%20dysfunctional%20for%20years%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FScreenshot-2022-07-07-155357_11zon-1696939453.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FScreenshot-2022-07-07-155357_11zon-1696939453-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FScreenshot-2022-07-07-155357_11zon-1696939453-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FScreenshot-2022-07-07-155357_11zon-1696939453-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FScreenshot-2022-07-07-155357_11zon-1696939453-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FScreenshot-2022-07-07-155357_11zon-1696939453-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331887%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20solar%20panels%20installed%20in%20the%20school%20are%20now%20used%20to%20power%20the%20computers%20that%20lay%20dysfunctional%20for%20years%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Nikhil%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESarita%2C%20a%20student%20of%20Class%206%20who%20loves%20spending%20time%20surfing%20the%20web%20at%20school%2C%20says%20she%20spends%20her%20time%20learning%20%E2%80%98Microsoft%20Paint%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98Word%E2%80%99%20among%20other%20applications%20on%20these%20refurbished%20computers%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%20now%20learn%20typing%20and%20do%20so%20much%20more.%20Otherwise%2C%20we%20had%20to%20go%2070%20km%20away%20from%20the%20village%20to%20use%20the%20computer%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20Nikhil%20has%20also%20helped%20the%20villagers%20learn%20bee%20farming%2C%20which%20further%20boosts%20their%20income.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20given%20them%20boxes%20which%20they%20use%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F175651%2Findia-beekeeping-pune-kvic-bee-conservation-diy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollect%20honey%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20villagers%20were%20able%20to%20sell%20the%20honey%20at%20Rs%20450%20per%20kg%20and%20we%20are%20now%20looking%20to%20help%20them%20sell%20their%20product%20directly%20to%20the%20markets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20as%20Nikhil%20attempts%20to%20expand%20his%20platform%20in%20the%20face%20of%20stiff%20competition%20from%20other%20similar%20businesses%2C%20he%20says%20his%20idea%20is%20rooted%20in%20a%20desire%20to%20see%20the%20people%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20villages%20uplifted.%20%E2%80%9CI%20hope%20I%E2%80%99m%20able%20to%20do%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20before%20signing%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696946015000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D331882%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nikhil%20Pratap%20Singh%20started%20'Planet%20Trotter'%20as%20a%20way%20to%20encourage